  ('01e68a59-b82c-4055-b029-8e6b48345bd8','C000027-A2','A2',null,'Thornchain Malison','Attacks all enemies. Has a 50% chance of placing a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn. Transfers a random debuff from this Champion to the targets that receive [Stun] debuffs from this skill.','4','3','0.35','HP',0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; verbatim 2026-07-10; re-keyed L0003->C000027'),
  ('01e68a59-b82c-4055-b029-8e6b48345bd8','C000027-A3','A3',null,'Warped Guidance','Places a 50% [Ally Protection] buff on all allies except this Champion for 2 turns. Also places a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 2 turns.','5','3',null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; verbatim 2026-07-10; re-keyed L0003->C000027'),
  ('01e68a59-b82c-4055-b029-8e6b48345bd8','C000027-Passive','Passive',null,'Cynical [P]','Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 5% each time an ally inflicts a critical hit. Heals this Champion by 5% of their MAX HP each time an enemy inflicts a critical hit.',null,null,null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; verbatim 2026-07-10; re-keyed L0003->C000027'),
  ('62f4ab1d-c2ca-4b01-9f1d-591eba164371','C000569-A1','A1',null,'Thorn Maul','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 30% chance of placing a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn. Also heals the ally with the lowest HP by 15% of the damage inflicted. The [Provoke] debuff can be placed even if this attack lands as a weak hit.',null,null,'0.25','HP',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('62f4ab1d-c2ca-4b01-9f1d-591eba164371','C000569-A2','A2',null,'Admonition of Barbs','Attacks all enemies 2 times. The first hit has a 75% chance of placing a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn. The second hit has a 75% chance of placing a [Leech] debuff for 2 turns. Also places a 25% [Strengthen] buff on this Champion.','4','3','0.15','HP',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('62f4ab1d-c2ca-4b01-9f1d-591eba164371','C000569-A3','A3',null,'Briar Nexus','Attacks all enemies. Damage increases by 5% for each debuff on each enemy. Also heals all allies by 20% of the damage inflicted and places a [Shield] buff on them for 2 turns equal to 20% of the damage inflicted.','5','4','0.25 HP * (1 + 0.05 * debuffs on enemy)','formula',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('62f4ab1d-c2ca-4b01-9f1d-591eba164371','C000569-Passive','Passive',null,'Dethorned','Decreases the damage taken by all allies from enemies under [Provoke] debuffs by 15%.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('a25dfaad-e8e8-4031-9ecf-56d334029eb7','S000004','A1',null,'Hammer of Kaerok','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 50% chance of placing a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn. Will ignore 25% of the target''s RES if this Champion is under a [Shield] buff.',null,null,null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','AyumiLove lines 104-136; HellHades corroborates shield/stun/protection kit.'),
  ('a25dfaad-e8e8-4031-9ecf-56d334029eb7','S000005','A2',null,'Shield Crush','Heals all allies by the total value of all [Shield]s on all allies. Then removes all [Shield]s from all allies and attacks all enemies. The damage dealt by this attack is equal to the total value of the [Shield]s removed (damage cannot exceed 1000% of this Champion''s DEF).','4','3',null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Faction Unity notes retained in summary/effects.'),
  ('a25dfaad-e8e8-4031-9ecf-56d334029eb7','S000006','A3',null,'Behold the Banner','Places a [Shield] buff equal to 30% of this Champion''s HP on all allies for 2 turns, and a 50% [Ally Protection] buff on all allies except this Champion for 2 turns. [Banner Lords Unity] 1 Faction Ally: Instantly activates this skill whenever an ally is revived. Will not put the skill on cooldown. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. 2 Faction Ally: Also places a [Block Damage] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. 3 Faction Ally: Buffs placed by this skill cannot be removed.','5','3',null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Unity mechanics summarized.'),
  ('a25dfaad-e8e8-4031-9ecf-56d334029eb7','S000007','Passive',null,'Knight of Knights','Allies under [Shield] buffs receive 10% less damage. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. [Banner Lords Unity] 1 Faction Ally: Allies under [Shield] buffs are immune to [Stun], [Freeze], [Sleep], [Provoke], [Fear], [True Fear], and [Petrification] debuff. 2 Faction Ally: Allies under [Ally Protection] buffs have a 20% chance of counterattacking when hit. 3 Faction Ally: The values of all ally [Shield] buffs are increased by 100%, except [Shield] buffs granted by Artifact Sets.',null,null,null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Passive has Unity bonuses.'),
  ('39ad1a06-13d7-43d3-9f2a-a16f89a54ec6','S000012','A1',null,'Bludgeon','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 25% chance of increasing the duration of all debuffs on the target by 1 turn.','0','0',null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','fandom_wiki. Books +5% / +10% Damage. No debuff placed on the enemy. | [cooldown back-calc 2026-07-10: filled base=0, booked=0 from Skills_Raw]'),
  ('39ad1a06-13d7-43d3-9f2a-a16f89a54ec6','S000013','A2',null,'Protection of Gods','Places a [Block Debuffs] buff on all allies for 1 turn. Places a [Shield] buff equal to this Champion''s MAX HP on all allies for 2 turns. Restores all allies'' HP by 25%.','4','3',null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','fandom_wiki. AoE ally protection: Block Debuffs + Shield (= MAX HP) + 25% heal. No books.'),
  ('39ad1a06-13d7-43d3-9f2a-a16f89a54ec6','S000014','A3',null,'Orcish Rituals','Attacks all enemies. Has a 70% chance to put each target''s Skills on cooldown. Has a 30% chance to fully deplete each target''s Turn Meter.','6','5',null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','fandom_wiki. Books +5/+5/+10/+10 chance. AoE Block Cooldowns (70%) + Decrease Turn Meter (30%). | [cooldown back-calc 2026-07-10: base held booked value; corrected base 5->6, booked=5 from Skills_Raw]'),
  ('c3328667-03e3-4223-87a5-6f6b63335428','C000316-A1','A1',null,'Necrotic Bolt','Attacks 1 enemy. Destroys the target''s MAX HP by 30% of the damage inflicted.',null,null,null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','In-game Index, Lvl 1 unbooked. MAX HP destroy = 30% of damage inflicted. Books: +5% Dmg L2-L5. Screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
  ('c3328667-03e3-4223-87a5-6f6b63335428','C000316-A2','A2',null,'Death''s Majesty','Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on this Champion for 2 turns, then attacks all enemies. Has a 50% chance of placing a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns.','4','3',null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','In-game Index, Lvl 1 unbooked. Increase ATK is SELF. Decrease SPD 50% unbooked -> 75% booked. Books: +5% Dmg L2, +10% Dmg L3, +10% Chance L4, +15% Chance L5, Cooldown -1 L6 (4->3). NOTE: seed-15 said 25% chance; in-game shows 50%. Screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
  ('c3328667-03e3-4223-87a5-6f6b63335428','C000316-P1','Passive',null,'Lethal Winter','Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 25% and instantly activates the Death''s Majesty skill whenever this Champion or an ally receives a [Freeze] debuff.','1',null,null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Passive [P], Level 1/1, cd 1t. FREEZE-REACTIVE: triggers when she/an ally RECEIVES [Freeze] (self TM fill + re-cast Death''s Majesty). Does NOT place Freeze. Screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
  ('c3328667-03e3-4223-87a5-6f6b63335428','C000316-P2','Passive',null,'Veins of Ice','Instantly removes any [Freeze] debuffs on this Champion and replaces them with a 30% [Increase C.RATE] buff, a 30% [Increase C.DMG] buff, and a 15% [Strengthen] buff whenever an enemy places a [Freeze] debuff on this Champion.','1',null,null,null,3,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Passive [P], Level 1/1, cd 1t. UNLOCKS AT ASCENSION LEVEL 3. Self buffs, triggered when an enemy Freezes her. Screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
  ('a1b39eef-2e0f-46c9-9b0b-77712f6f1648','C000392-A1','A1',null,'Monk''s Spade','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 45% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,'0.24','HP',0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','In-game Index, Lvl 1 unbooked. Chance 45% unbooked -> 60% booked (+5% Dmg L2, +5% Chance L3, +10% Dmg L4, +10% Chance L5). NOTE: raid.guide/seed-15 said 30% unbooked; in-game shows 45%. Screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
  ('a1b39eef-2e0f-46c9-9b0b-77712f6f1648','C000392-A2','A2',null,'Fated Duel','Places a [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns equal to 25% of their MAX HP, then attacks 1 enemy. Places a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn. If the target''s MAX HP is equal to or lower than this Champion''s, the [Provoke] debuff cannot be resisted.','4','3','0.32','HP',0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','In-game Index, Lvl 1 unbooked. Shield is SELF (25% of his MAX HP). Books through L8; Cooldown -1 at L8 (4->3). Screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
  ('a1b39eef-2e0f-46c9-9b0b-77712f6f1648','C000392-A3','A3',null,'True Smite','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore 25% of the target''s DEF. Will also ignore [Unkillable] and [Block Damage] buffs.','4','3','0.34','HP',0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','In-game Index, Lvl 1 unbooked. IGNORES enemy [Unkillable]/[Block Damage] buffs (does NOT place them) + ignores 25% DEF. Books: +5% Dmg L2, +5% Dmg L3, +10% Dmg L4, Cooldown -1 L5 (4->3). Screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
  ('a1b39eef-2e0f-46c9-9b0b-77712f6f1648','C000392-P','Passive',null,'Smiles at Death','Will receive 25% less damage from enemy attacks when this Champion''s HP drops to 50% or below.',null,null,null,null,3,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Passive [P], Level 1/1. UNLOCKS AT ASCENSION LEVEL 3. Self damage mitigation. In-game Index, screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
  ('677f9085-f120-46db-85c8-65f32298d153','C000701-A1','A1',null,'Envenomed Sickles','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 15% chance of increasing the duration of all enemy debuffs by 1 turn. If the 2nd hit does not increase the duration of all enemy debuffs, instantly activates all [Poison] debuffs on the target instead.',null,null,null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','In-game Index skill popup, Lvl 1 unbooked, screen recording 2026-07-07. Books: L2 Damage +20%, L3 Buff/Debuff Chance +10%, L4 Buff/Debuff Chance +15%.'),
  ('677f9085-f120-46db-85c8-65f32298d153','C000701-A2','A2',null,'They Will Regret...','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The first hit has a 75% chance of placing a 25% [Poison Sensitivity] debuff and two 5% [Poison] debuffs for 2 turns. The second hit applies a [Debuff Spread] effect, taking all [Poison] debuffs and the [Poison Sensitivity] debuff from the target and placing them on all other enemies.','4','3',null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','In-game Index skill popup, Lvl 1 unbooked, screen recording 2026-07-07. Books: L2 Damage +20%, L3 Buff/Debuff Chance +10%, L4 Buff/Debuff Chance +15%, L5 Cooldown -1 (4->3).'),
  ('677f9085-f120-46db-85c8-65f32298d153','C000701-A3','A3',null,'Toxic Vitriol','Attacks all enemies. Places a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Increases this Champion''s Turn Meter by 20% for each [Decrease ATK] debuff placed. Instantly activates all [Poison] debuffs on all enemies.','4','3',null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','In-game Index skill popup, Lvl 1 unbooked, screen recording 2026-07-07. Books: L2 Damage +10%, L3 Damage +10%, L4 Cooldown -1 (4->3).'),
  ('677f9085-f120-46db-85c8-65f32298d153','C000701-P','Passive',null,'Imbibed Immunity','This Champion is immune to [Poison], [Stun], and [Decrease SPD] debuffs. Increases this Champion''s damage dealt by 5% (stacks up to 50%) and Ignore DEF effect by 3% (stacks up to 30%) for each active debuff on the enemy team. Whenever this Champion is attacked by an enemy under a debuff placed by this Champion, counterattacks using their default skill.',null,null,null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Passive [P], Level 1/1, not ascension-gated. In-game Index skill popup, screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
  ('67fe889a-0a79-4c71-84f1-7279415187f8','C000468-A1','A1',null,'Harassment Volley','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. Each critical hit has an 80% chance of stealing 5% of the target''s Turn Meter.',null,null,null,null,0,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','In-game Index, Lvl 1 unbooked. TM steal is conditional (crit + 80%). Books: +5% Dmg L2, +5% Chance L3, +5% Dmg L4, +5% Chance L5, +10% Chance L6. Screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
