  ('67fe889a-0a79-4c71-84f1-7279415187f8','C000468-A3','A3',null,'Timed Offensive','Fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 20% and places a 30% [Increase C.RATE] buff on all allies for 2 turns.','6','3',null,null,3,'verified','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','UNLOCKS AT ASCENSION LEVEL 3. Ally-facing team buff (TM fill + C.RATE). Books: Cooldown -1 L2-L4 (6->3). Screen recording 2026-07-07.'),
