  ('970391a3-3264-4db0-bcd3-a3eda6610042','C000023-A4','A4',null,'Pirate Lord [P]','[Passive Effect] At the start of each Round, places a [Perfect Veil] buff on this Champion for 1 turn. Has a 20% chance to reflect all damage and debuffs this Champion receives back to the attacker. Will only work on skills that inflict damage, or inflict damage and place debuffs. Does not work against Bosses. [Active Effect] If the reflected damage kills an enemy, fills this Champion’s Turn Meter by 30% and places a [Perfect Veil] buff on this Champion for 1 turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('0410728c-0855-46e0-8910-489d38b3f762','C000024-A1','A1',null,'Hexbloom','Attacks 1 enemy. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 10%. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by an additional 10% if the enemy is under a [Hex] debuff. Will counterattack using this skill when hit by enemies under a [Hex] debuff. This skill also deals 50% more damage when counterattacking.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('0410728c-0855-46e0-8910-489d38b3f762','C000024-A2','A2',null,'Capricious Spite','Attacks all enemies 2 times. Damage increases by 15% for each enemy under a [Hex] debuff. Will ignore [Shield], [Block Damage], and [Strengthen] buffs. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 30%. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by an additional 20% for each enemy killed by this skill.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('0410728c-0855-46e0-8910-489d38b3f762','C000024-A3','A3',null,'Mindsnare Cloud','Places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Has a 75% chance of placing a [Deathbrand] debuff on a target enemy for 2 turns. Also has a 75% chance of placing a [Hex] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Will ignore [Block Debuffs] buffs. Also places a protected [Block Damage] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Then grants an Extra Turn.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('0410728c-0855-46e0-8910-489d38b3f762','C000024-P','Passive',null,'Fanglilac Frenzy [P]','Whenever this Champion kills an enemy in a battle, will ignore 10% of any target''s DEF. (stacks up to 30%). Whenever this Champion kills 2 or more enemies in a battle, this Champion will receive a [Shield] buff for 2 turns at the end of their own turn. The value of the [Shield] is equal to 400% of this Champion''s ATK. Whenever this Champion kills 3 or more enemies in a battle, places a [Block Revive] debuff on any subsequent enemies killed by this Champion.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('0ce1d01b-2328-4e3a-a1ed-556365c57a95','C000050-A1','A1',null,'Arcane Dynamo','Attacks 1 enemy. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 10%. Fills the Turn Meter by 20% if this attack is critical.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('0ce1d01b-2328-4e3a-a1ed-556365c57a95','C000050-A2','A2',null,'Timeslip','Attacks 1 enemy. Also attacks all other enemies if the first attack is critical. The second hit has a 50% chance of placing a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn. After attacking, decreases the Turn Meters of each enemy without a [Stun] debuff by 20%.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('0ce1d01b-2328-4e3a-a1ed-556365c57a95','C000050-A3','A3',null,'Psychic Guidance','Places a 30% [Increase SPD] buff, a 30% [Increase C. RATE] buff, and a 30% [Increase C. DMG] buff on all allies for 2 turns.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('0ce1d01b-2328-4e3a-a1ed-556365c57a95','C000050-A4','A4',null,'Chrono Isolation [P]','Immune to Turn Meter reduction effects from enemies.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7b64076f-b070-4b76-a26d-d5b6150a24ed','C000028-A1','A1',null,'Wyrd Blade','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 35% chance of increasing the cooldown of a random active skill by 2 turns. Fills this Champion’s Turn Meter by 10% for each turn added to the cooldown.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7b64076f-b070-4b76-a26d-d5b6150a24ed','C000028-A2','A2',null,'Greatest Hits','Attacks all enemies. Steals all the Turn Meter of each target, except enemies under [Sheep] debuffs. Also places a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn on all enemies not under a [Sheep] debuff.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7b64076f-b070-4b76-a26d-d5b6150a24ed','C000028-A3','A3',null,'For My Next Trick!','Places a [Sheep] debuff on an enemy for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be blocked. Then, has a 75% chance of removing all buffs from all enemies. Fills this Champion’s Turn Meter by 5% for each buff removed.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7b64076f-b070-4b76-a26d-d5b6150a24ed','C000028-P','Passive',null,'Master of Ceremonies [P]','Whenever a [Sheep] debuff is removed or expires on an enemy, increase the cooldown of a random active skill on that enemy to its max. Fills this Champion’s Turn Meter by 10% for each turn added to the cooldown. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This skill will not activate on duplicate copies of this Champion, if this particular Champion is dead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('18a3bff5-525a-4f68-b5f6-a8704e118404','C000052-A1','A1',null,'Iron Greatclub','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 20% chance of placing a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('18a3bff5-525a-4f68-b5f6-a8704e118404','C000052-A2','A2',null,'Daunting Violence','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. Also has a 25% chance of placing a [Fear] debuff for 1 turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('18a3bff5-525a-4f68-b5f6-a8704e118404','C000052-A3','A3',null,'Wall of Metal','Places a 30% [Reflect Damage] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 2 turns.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('20200d61-bc07-4e8b-897d-7de91158df4f','C000029-A1','A1',null,'Shining Cleave','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Damage increases by 5% for each buff on the target. Each hit has a 35% chance of placing a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('20200d61-bc07-4e8b-897d-7de91158df4f','C000029-A2','A2',null,'Glimmerforce','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. The damage inflicted by this skill increases by 10% for each 10% HP this Champion has lost. If the target is under 2 or more buffs, will also ignore 35% of the target''s DEF. Grants an Extra Turn if this attack kills an enemy.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('20200d61-bc07-4e8b-897d-7de91158df4f','C000029-A3','A3',null,'Wrath of Hrothglime','Attacks all enemies. Will ignore [Increase DEF], [Strengthen] and [Shield] buffs. If this attack kills at least 1 enemy, decreases the Turn Meters of all enemies by 50%. This effect cannot be resisted.','6 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('20200d61-bc07-4e8b-897d-7de91158df4f','C000029-A4','A4',null,'Golden King [P]','[Passive Effect] Increases this Champion’s ATK by 5% for each active buff on the enemy team (stacks up to 100%). [Active Effect] Prevents this Champion’s death and keep them alive on 1 HP when hit by a fatal hit. Places a [Stone Skin] buff on them for 1 turn. Then, instantly activates the [Wrath of Hrothglime] skill. This will not place the [Wrath of Hrothglime] skill on cooldown. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, this effect will only activate once.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('20072536-e08f-4782-b198-6a608144ba67','C000030-A1','A1',null,'Chaosrazor','Attacks all enemies. Has a 35% chance to extend the duration of any [HP Burn] debuffs on each target by 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('20072536-e08f-4782-b198-6a608144ba67','C000030-A2','A2',null,'Dogs of War','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, instantly activates one tick of all [HP Burn] debuffs on all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('20072536-e08f-4782-b198-6a608144ba67','C000030-A3','A3',null,'Purifyre','Attacks all enemies 2 times. The first hit has a 75% chance of placing a [HP Burn] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Restores this Champion’s destroyed MAX HP by 10% for each [HP Burn] debuff placed by this skill. Heals this Champion by 5% of their MAX HP for each [HP Burn] debuff attempt blocked or resisted by the enemy team.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('20072536-e08f-4782-b198-6a608144ba67','C000030-P','Passive',null,'Burning Blood [P]','Whenever a [HP Burn] debuff is activated, destroys this Champion’s MAX HP by 5%. Stacks up to 50%. Increases this Champion’s DMG, C. DMG, and DEF by 1% for each 1% of their destroyed MAX HP. Also increases this Champion’s SPD and RES by 2 for each 1% of their destroyed MAX HP.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('487efd8e-2710-4820-8cc4-308d6479705f','C000053-A1','A1',null,'Grasscutter','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 50% chance of stealing 1 random buff from the target.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('487efd8e-2710-4820-8cc4-308d6479705f','C000053-A2','A2',null,'Quivergrass Vortex','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, removes all debuffs from this Champion. Has a 75% chance of removing a random buff from all enemies.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('487efd8e-2710-4820-8cc4-308d6479705f','C000053-A3','A3',null,'Ax Leap','Attacks 1 enemy. Damage increases by 30% if this Champion has no active debuffs. Will also ignore [Unkillable] buffs if this Champion has no active debuffs.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('487efd8e-2710-4820-8cc4-308d6479705f','C000053-A4','A4',null,'Rippling Grass [P]','This Champion’s ACC is increased by 50 if they have no active debuffs.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('a9504e74-b2cc-4a3a-aa41-0fea63d09d0e','C000033-A1','A1',null,'Zephyr of Conquest','Attacks all enemies. Has a 50% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('a9504e74-b2cc-4a3a-aa41-0fea63d09d0e','C000033-A2','A2',null,'Dread Dominion','Has a 75% chance to place a [Block Buffs] debuff and a [True Fear] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. If the target is a Boss, has a 75% chance to place a [Block Buffs] debuff and a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff on them instead.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('a9504e74-b2cc-4a3a-aa41-0fea63d09d0e','C000033-A3','A3',null,'Icon of Domination','Removes all debuffs from a single ally (except this Champion) and places 2 [Intercept] stacks on them. Also fills the target ally’s Turn Meter by 50% and resets the cooldowns of all their skills.','6 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('a9504e74-b2cc-4a3a-aa41-0fea63d09d0e','C000033-A4','A4',null,'Authority Manifest [P]','This Champion is immune to [Sheep] debuffs. Each debuff placed by this Champion decreases a target''s Turn Meter by 5% and permanently decreases their RES and ACC by 10 (stacks up to 100).',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7db82fda-0f5b-4d2f-9cef-e338238144c4','C000558-A1','A1',null,'Fierce Friend','Attacks 1 enemy. Places one 15% [Continuous Heal] buff on this Champion and the ally with the lowest HP, excluding this Champion, for 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7db82fda-0f5b-4d2f-9cef-e338238144c4','C000558-A2','A2',null,'Thieving Axeman','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. The first hit has a 75% chance of stealing all buffs from the target. The second hit transfers all debuffs from this Champion to the target. The third hit applies a [Debuff Spread] effect, taking all debuffs from the target and placing them on all other enemies.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7db82fda-0f5b-4d2f-9cef-e338238144c4','C000558-A3','A3',null,'Bucklan''s Strength','Attacks all enemies. Places a [Provoke] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. Has 75% chance to place a [Pain Link] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. The [Pain Link] debuff reflects 45% of the inflicted damage. Also places a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion and the ally with the highest C. DMG for 2 turns.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7db82fda-0f5b-4d2f-9cef-e338238144c4','C000558-A4','A4',null,'Disciple of Padraig [P]','Heals all allies by 40% of any damage dealt to this Champion. At the end of this Champion’s turn, places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff on this Champion for 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('9881d6d5-a6f9-4000-a5a8-ae3659a805b0','C000559-A1','A1',null,'Malignant Thorns','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, places a [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s ATK. Has a 50% chance of placing a 25% [Poison Sensitivity] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('9881d6d5-a6f9-4000-a5a8-ae3659a805b0','C000559-A2','A2',null,'Twyster of Life','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 75% chance of placing a [Leech] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Instantly activates all [Poison] debuffs on all enemies.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('9881d6d5-a6f9-4000-a5a8-ae3659a805b0','C000559-A3','A3',null,'Monstrous Growth','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Has a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease RES] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Places three 5% [Poison] debuffs on the initial target for 2 turns. If this attack is critical, places three 5% [Poison] debuffs for 2 turns on all enemies instead.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('9881d6d5-a6f9-4000-a5a8-ae3659a805b0','C000559-P','Passive',null,'Lost to Chaos [P]','Increases this Champion’s Ignore DEF effect by 1% for each [Poison] debuff instantly activated by this Champion (stacks up to 20%). Fills this Champion’s Turn Meter by 5% whenever a [Poison] debuff is placed on an enemy.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('98401e02-3594-43b2-8d41-0a0c0011a8ce','C000560-A1','A1',null,'Bamboo Splinter','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 75% chance of placing a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns. Will attack all enemies instead if the initial target is under 2 or more debuffs. This attack has a 75% chance of placing a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns. Then places a [Sleep] debuff on this Champion for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be blocked or resisted.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('98401e02-3594-43b2-8d41-0a0c0011a8ce','C000560-A2','A2',null,'Grovetender','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a [Shield] buff on all allies equal to 30% of this Champion''s MAX HP for 2 turns. Also increases the duration of all buffs on all allies by 1 turn. After attacking, has a 75% chance of decreasing the duration of all enemy buffs by 1 turn, even if the attack lands as a weak hit. Also increases the value of any [Shield] buffs on all allies by 3% for each enemy buff that had its duration decreased by this skill. Then places a [Sleep] debuff on this Champion for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be blocked or resisted.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('98401e02-3594-43b2-8d41-0a0c0011a8ce','C000560-A3','A3',null,'Dream Sight','Target an enemy. First, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff and a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Then, has a 75% chance of placing an [Enfeeble] debuff and a 50% [Decrease ACC] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. The [Enfeeble] debuff cannot be placed on Bosses. Has a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff on Bosses for 2 turns instead. Finally, places a [Sleep] debuff on this Champion for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be blocked or resisted.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('98401e02-3594-43b2-8d41-0a0c0011a8ce','C000560-P','Passive',null,'Sleeping Sage [P]','[Passive Effect] Has a 75% chance of transferring any debuffs placed on an ally to this Champion while they are under a [Sleep] debuff. Will not transfer [Block Revive], [Stun], [Freeze], [Fear], [True Fear], [Provoke], [Petrification], and [Sheep] debuffs. At the start of this Champion''s turn, remove any [Sleep] debuffs from this Champion. [Active Effect] Transfers all debuffs from this Champion to the enemy with the highest RES if a [Sleep] debuff was removed from this Champion by this Champion''s passive skill or by an enemy attack. This effect cannot be resisted or blocked.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7c314984-8076-4dd2-8b70-1fd62458529f','C000563-A1','A1',null,'Dagger Swirl','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 50% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. If this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff, the chance increases to 100%. Then has a 50% chance of applying a [Debuff Spread] effect, taking 1 random debuff from the target and placing it on all enemies. If this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff, the chance increases to 100%.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7c314984-8076-4dd2-8b70-1fd62458529f','C000563-A2','A2',null,'Up In Smoke','Attacks all enemies. Will ignore 15% of each target’s DEF. Will ignore 30% of each target’s DEF instead if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff. Has a 75% chance of placing a [Block Active Skills] debuff for 2 turns. This debuff will ignore any [Block Debuffs] buffs if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7c314984-8076-4dd2-8b70-1fd62458529f','C000563-A3','A3',null,'Winds of Baghdad','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Deals 5% more damage for each buff and debuff on this Champion and 5% more damage for each buff and debuff on the target (stacks up to 100%). Places a [Perfect Veil] buff on this Champion for 3 turns, and grants an Extra Turn.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7c314984-8076-4dd2-8b70-1fd62458529f','C000563-P','Passive',null,'Everything Is Permitted [P]','Whenever an enemy’s HP drops below 25% after receiving damage from any Assassin, they receive additional bonus damage proportional to this Champion’s ATK. This bonus damage will ignore 100% of the target’s DEF and cannot be critical.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7c314984-8076-4dd2-8b70-1fd62458529f','C000563-P2','Passive 2',null,'Masterful Thief [P]','Whenever this Champion is attacked, steals 1 random buff from the attacker and transfers 1 random debuff from this Champion to the attacker. These effects will ignore [Polymorph]. Occurs once per skill. Will ignore 25% of a target''s RES when using skills if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
