  ('7c74d1f1-30df-47f9-a827-b86463fdcc82','C000332-A2','A2',null,'Cannibal Litany','Places a 30% [Reflect Damage] buff on all allies for 2 turns, a 15% [Continuous Heal] buff on all allies for 1 turn, then heals all allies by 15% of their MAX HP.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
