  ('3fd85f24-33c1-46af-bdb9-845dc30b42f2','C000607-A1','A1',null,'Hawkstrike','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 75% chance of stealing 15% of the target’s Turn Meter. Also has a 75% chance of applying a [Debuff Spread] effect, taking 2 random debuffs from the target and placing them on all enemies.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('3fd85f24-33c1-46af-bdb9-845dc30b42f2','C000607-A2','A2',null,'The Herald Speaks','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, has a 75% chance of stealing all buffs from the target enemy. Then applies a [Buff Spread] effect, taking all buffs from this Champion and placing them on all allies. Places a [Block Buffs] debuff and a [Block Active Skills] debuff on the target for 2 turns.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('3fd85f24-33c1-46af-bdb9-845dc30b42f2','C000607-A3','A3',null,'Booming Voice','Places 1 [Intercept] stack on a target ally. Also places a [Block Debuffs] buff and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on all allies for 2 turns.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('3fd85f24-33c1-46af-bdb9-845dc30b42f2','C000607-P','Passive',null,'Wings of Victory [P]','At the start of the round, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 3 turns. Whenever a debuff on an enemy is removed, expires, or has its duration decreased, fills this Champion’s Turn Meter by 5%.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('2989fb5a-a1f5-473b-9b13-315e660afc2e','C000608-A1','A1',null,'Axe of Unity','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 100% chance of placing a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn. If the [Provoke] debuff is placed, the ally with the highest C.DMG will team up and join this Champion in an attack.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('2989fb5a-a1f5-473b-9b13-315e660afc2e','C000608-A2','A2',null,'Sandstorm Shield','Removes all buffs from all enemies, then places a [Shield] buff on all allies for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s DEF.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('2989fb5a-a1f5-473b-9b13-315e660afc2e','C000608-A3','A3',null,'Rallying Cry','Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff, a 50% [Increase ACC] buff, and a 60% [Increase DEF] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also reduces the cooldown of all ally skills by 1 turn, fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 20%, and grants an [Instant Turn] to the ally with the highest C.DMG.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('2989fb5a-a1f5-473b-9b13-315e660afc2e','C000608-A4','A4',null,'Desert''s Fury','Has a 50% chance of placing a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn on an attacker when hit. [Unity Bonus]: Increases damage dealt by allies to targets under crowd control debuffs. Allies ignore 50% of enemy RES when placing crowd control debuffs. Debuffs and instant effects applied outside of a Champion''s turn or during an [Instant Turn] or [Extra Turn] cannot be resisted.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('2f29c0bf-7e5d-4bd1-9cf4-717e11728c4c','C000333-A1','A1',null,'Firefly Hatchet','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 25% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('2f29c0bf-7e5d-4bd1-9cf4-717e11728c4c','C000333-A2','A2',null,'Moonlight Ambuscade','Teams up with 2 random allies to attack a single enemy. The allies joining the attack will use their default skills. If the target is under a [Decrease DEF] debuff, these attacks will ignore 20% of the target’s DEF.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('2f29c0bf-7e5d-4bd1-9cf4-717e11728c4c','C000333-A3','A3',null,'Covert Blitz','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 30% [Increase C. RATE] buff and a 30% [Increase C. DMG] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. If this attack kills an enemy, places a [Veil] buff on all allies for 1 turn.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('2f29c0bf-7e5d-4bd1-9cf4-717e11728c4c','C000333-A4','A4',null,'Gloompiercer [P]','This Champion will ignore [Shield] and [Strengthen] buffs when attacking under an [Increase ATK], [Veil], or [Perfect Veil] buff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('6d6389f5-dbd3-42e1-ad99-5a81717a59bc','C000609-A1','A1',null,'Privateer Blitz','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. Each hit has a 75% chance of decreasing the target’s Turn Meter by 15%. Each hit will decrease the target’s Turn Meter by 25% instead if the attack is critical. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('6d6389f5-dbd3-42e1-ad99-5a81717a59bc','C000609-A2','A2',null,'Fan The Hammer','Attacks all enemies 2 times. The first hit steals all buffs from all enemies and decreases each enemy''s Turn Meter by 20%. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff. The second hit has a 75% chance of placing a [Sleep] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. This debuff will ignore any [Block Debuffs] buffs if the attack is critical. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('6d6389f5-dbd3-42e1-ad99-5a81717a59bc','C000609-A3','A3',null,'Between The Eyes','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, places a [Perfect Veil] buff on this Champion, as well as any other Assassins on the team for 2 turns. Will ignore [Shield], [Stone Skin], and [Block Damage] buffs. Places a [Block Revive] debuff if the target is killed.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
