  ('00404172-1b85-49eb-b353-a0aaaf9cca1f','C000618-A1','A1',null,'Eagle Dive','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 75% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('00404172-1b85-49eb-b353-a0aaaf9cca1f','C000618-A2','A2',null,'Da Vinci''s Design','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing two 5% [Poison] debuffs and a 25% [Poison Sensitivity] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. These debuffs cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff. Instantly activates all [Poison] debuffs on enemies under 4 or more debuffs. If any enemies are under a [Stone Skin] buff, has a 75% chance of placing 2 [Bomb] debuffs that detonate after 2 turns on them instead. These debuffs cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff. If all enemies are under a [Stone Skin] buff, decreases each [Bomb] debuff’s detonation countdown by 1 turn.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('00404172-1b85-49eb-b353-a0aaaf9cca1f','C000618-A3','A3',null,'Hidden Gun','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, steals all buffs from the target. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff. Will ignore 35% of the target’s DEF, as well as [Shield] and [Strengthen] buffs.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('00404172-1b85-49eb-b353-a0aaaf9cca1f','C000618-P','Passive',null,'Everything Is Permitted [P]','Whenever an enemy’s HP drops below 25% after receiving damage from any Assassin, they receive additional bonus damage proportional to this Champion’s ATK. This bonus damage will ignore 100% of the target’s DEF and cannot be critical.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('00404172-1b85-49eb-b353-a0aaaf9cca1f','C000618-P2','Passive 2',null,'Full Synchronization [P]','Places a [Perfect Veil] buff on this Champion for 2 turns at the start of each Round. Whenever this Champion is about to receive damage that would exceed 50% of their MAX HP, has a 35% chance of decreasing the damage received to 0 instead. Whenever this Champion is attacked, also has a 35% chance of counterattacking.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7060d2de-4936-456e-bb0d-24c3eea93c0f','C000619-A1','A1',null,'Mournsword','Attacks 1 enemy. Heals this Champion by 50% of the damage inflicted. If there is any surplus heal, places a [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns equal to the surplus heal. Will attack using the Burning Courage skill instead if the target is from the Corrupted Alliance.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('7060d2de-4936-456e-bb0d-24c3eea93c0f','C000619-A2','A2',null,'In Lumaya''s Name','Attack all enemies. Damage inflicted by this skill increases by 5% for each buff and debuff on the target. Will ignore 25% DEF of targets that have no buffs.','3',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
