  ('a975b9d8-4349-4314-a36e-995a26685105','C000631-A1','A1',null,'Seal Scroll','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 30% chance of placing a [Block Active Skills] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('a975b9d8-4349-4314-a36e-995a26685105','C000631-A2','A2',null,'Thief of Blood','Attacks all enemies. Has an 80% chance of stealing all buffs from each enemy. After stealing, applies a [Buff Spread] effect, taking all buffs from this Champion and placing them on all allies.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('a975b9d8-4349-4314-a36e-995a26685105','C000631-A3','A3',null,'Dread Invocation','Can target dead or living enemies. If the target is dead, places [Block Revive] on them, then attacks all enemies. Each enemy will receive damage equal to 20% of the target enemy''s MAX HP. If the target is a Boss'' minion, the damage is equal to 20% of this Champion''s MAX HP. This attack cannot be critical, and will ignore any [Shield] buffs and 100% of each target''s DEF. If the target is alive, places a [True Fear] debuff on them for 2 turns and heals all allies by 20% of the target enemy''s MAX HP. If the target is a Boss or a Boss'' minion, the healing is equal to 20% of this Champion''s MAX HP. The [True Fear] debuff cannot be resisted.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('a975b9d8-4349-4314-a36e-995a26685105','C000631-A4','A4',null,'Soul Charge [P]','Revives 1 random ally with 30% HP and 30% Turn Meter each time an enemy is killed. Revives 1 random ally with 30% HP and 30% Turn Meter each time a [Block Revive] debuff is placed on an enemy.','2 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
