  ('94937ec1-f1eb-4a67-ab52-dccbf82767d8','C000357-A2','A2',null,'Creeping Petrify','Removes all buffs from a target enemy, then attacks them. Steals all buffs instead if the target is under a [HP Burn] debuff placed by this Champion. Reduces the cooldown of Quicksand Grasp by 2 turns if the target is killed by this Skill while under a [HP Burn] debuff placed by this Champion.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('94937ec1-f1eb-4a67-ab52-dccbf82767d8','C000357-A3','A3',null,'Quicksand Grasp','Fully depletes the target’s Turn Meter. Fills this Champion’s Turn Meter by the amount the target loses. Has a 75% chance of placing a [HP Burn] and a 25% [Weaken] debuff on the target for 3 turns.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
