  ('fb236e91-0f10-4dba-8dba-12c282094914','C000639-P','Passive',null,'Timeless [P]','This Champion''s skills cannot be put on cooldown. Whenever an enemy tries to put either this Champion''s skills or an ally''s skills on cooldown, places a [Freeze] debuff on that enemy. The [Freeze] debuff cannot be blocked or resisted. Also has a 50% chance of denying the cooldown increase effect. That chance increases by 25% for each enemy under a [Freeze] debuff. Will not deny cooldown increasing effects from Bosses. Whenever an enemy tries to put either this Champion''s skills or an ally''s skills on cooldown, activates an [Instant Turn] effect on this Champion. Occurs once per turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('95853c5c-716f-488f-bd92-5d9066bf9a06','C000640-A1','A1',null,'Spear of Serenity','Attacks 1 enemy with 1 random ally from the Argonites Faction. The ally joining the attack will use their default skill. Heals all allies by 10% of this Champion’s MAX HP.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
