  ('06361a47-8396-499d-a528-9b2c138ded2b','C000653-A3','A3',null,'Fires of Auld','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a [HP Burn] debuff for 2 turns. Also fills this Champion’s Turn Meter by 5% for every [HP Burn] debuff the enemy team had before this attack.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('06361a47-8396-499d-a528-9b2c138ded2b','C000653-A4','A4',null,'Keeper of Flame [P]','[Passive Effect] This Champion will not receive any damage from [HP Burn] debuffs. Instead, [HP Burn] debuffs will heal this Champion by 5% MAX HP each time the debuff activates. [Active Effect] Whenever an enemy attempts to place a [Freeze] debuff on this Champion, instantly removes it and places it on the attacker. Also places a [HP Burn] debuff on the attacker for 1 turn. The [HP Burn] debuff cannot be resisted.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('d2f1c322-4d5c-4030-a9d0-dc1cc10aadc5','C000654-A1','A1',null,'If Looks Could Kill','Attacks all enemies. Places an extra hit on targets whose ATK is less than or equal to this Champion’s.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('d2f1c322-4d5c-4030-a9d0-dc1cc10aadc5','C000654-A2','A2',null,'Siroth''s Favoured','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, equalizes the HP of all enemies. The HP levels of all enemies will be set to the average of the enemy team. Will ignore 30% of each target''s DEF if the average HP of the enemy team is above 50%. Places an extra hit if the average HP of the enemy team is equal to or below 50%. Increases this Champion’s ATK by 10% per each enemy killed by this skill.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('d2f1c322-4d5c-4030-a9d0-dc1cc10aadc5','C000654-A3','A3',null,'Bloody Poleax','Attacks all enemies 2 times. Before attacking, places a 30% [Increase C. DMG] buff and a 15% [Shatter] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The first hit decreases each target’s DEF by 10% (stacks up to 30%). The second hit destroys each target''s MAX HP by 10% (stacks up to 60%). Grants an Extra Turn if this attack kills an enemy.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('d2f1c322-4d5c-4030-a9d0-dc1cc10aadc5','C000654-P','Passive',null,'Lover Of Slaughter [P]','Whenever this Champion lands a critical hit, heals them by 5% of their MAX HP. If this Champion’s HP is full, critical hits fill their Turn Meter by 5% instead. Whenever this Champion receives any surplus healing from this skill, places a [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns, equal to the value of the surplus heal. The value of the [Shield] cannot exceed 30% of this Champion’s MAX HP. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This skill will not activate on duplicate copies of this Champion, if this particular Champion is dead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('6adccc51-0535-4e55-842c-9af5c728c163','C000657-A1','A1',null,'Noxious Leeches','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 50% chance of placing a [Leech] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('6adccc51-0535-4e55-842c-9af5c728c163','C000657-A2','A2',null,'Rotlimb Decoction','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 100% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. After attacking, places two 5% [Poison] debuffs on the target for 2 turns if the [Weaken] debuff is not placed. These [Poison] debuffs cannot be resisted.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('6adccc51-0535-4e55-842c-9af5c728c163','C000657-A3','A3',null,'Hemlock Surprise','Attacks all enemies. Removes 1 random buff from each enemy. Also removes 2 random debuffs from all allies. Places two 5% [Poison] debuffs on all enemies for 2 turns.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('6adccc51-0535-4e55-842c-9af5c728c163','C000657-P','Passive',null,'Bog-Walker','Whenever an enemy receives a debuff, decreases their Turn Meter by 3%. This happens for each debuff placed.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
