  ('56a3d800-d457-4553-9ef6-3777db79cdb0','C000658-A3','A3',null,'Plumedart','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Has a 75% chance of stealing all [Block Debuffs] buffs from all enemies. If at least 1 [Block Debuffs] buff was stolen from the enemy, places a [Block Debuffs] buff on all allies for 1 turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
