  ('b4ee7163-16ac-4e5b-8558-15c0c2ae38cc','C000670-A2','A2',null,'Embittering Cold','Removes all buffs from all enemies, and places a [Freeze] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. If Tormin the Cold is on the same team, instantly activates his Blizzard Rage skill. This skill''s cooldown cannot be decreased or reset.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('b4ee7163-16ac-4e5b-8558-15c0c2ae38cc','C000670-A3','A3',null,'Ward Of The Glacier','Revives all dead allies with 50% HP and 30% Turn Meter. Places a [Block Damage] buff on all allies for 1 turn and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Will place these buffs even if no allies were revived. If no allies were revived by this skill, also fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 25%. This skill''s cooldown cannot be decreased or reset.','6',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
