  ('c8f61c77-9474-47fb-82bc-bb13a27faf21','C000686-A3','A3',null,'Soulscourge','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore [Unkillable], [Block Damage], and [Shield] buffs. Has a 100% chance of placing a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn. Resets the cooldown of this skill if the target is killed. If Yumeko is on the same team, this skill will also ignore 30% of the target''s DEF.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('c8f61c77-9474-47fb-82bc-bb13a27faf21','C000686-P','Passive',null,'Soul Reaper','This Champion''s damage bypasses all enemy Passive skills and Masteries that reduce damage. This passive does not work against Bosses. Also, this Champion''s damage is not increased by their own Passive skills or Masteries. If Yumeko is on the same team and is killed, instantly activates the Fox''s Cunning skill. This will not place the skill on cooldown.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('b29ed6ab-cf26-44e3-aca1-402d8d676e9c','C000687-A1','A1',null,'Deathknell','Attacks all enemies. Has a 35% chance of decreasing the duration of all enemy buffs by 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('b29ed6ab-cf26-44e3-aca1-402d8d676e9c','C000687-A2','A2',null,'Canticle of Cold','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a [Hex] debuff and a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. If the target is under a [Freeze] debuff, has a 75% chance of placing a [Hex] debuff and a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 3 turns instead.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('b29ed6ab-cf26-44e3-aca1-402d8d676e9c','C000687-A3','A3',null,'Polar Vortex','Places a [Freeze] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. Fully depletes the Turn Meters of all enemies that receive [Freeze] debuffs from this skill. Fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 10% for each [Freeze] debuff attempt blocked or resisted by the enemy team.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('b29ed6ab-cf26-44e3-aca1-402d8d676e9c','C000687-A4','A4',null,'Rime Hammer [P]','Allies will ignore 10% of the target''s DEF if the target is under [Freeze] debuffs. If the [Freeze] debuff was placed by this Champion, allies will ignore 20% of the target’s DEF instead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('db839513-9cb3-42a7-8a0b-2463d4785350','C000688-A1','A1',null,'Piercing Strikes','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. If this Champion is under a [Veil] buff and has less than 50% HP, attacks 6 times instead. Each hit irresistibly decreases the target''s Turn Meter by 7.5%.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('db839513-9cb3-42a7-8a0b-2463d4785350','C000688-A2','A2',null,'Debilitating Blow','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, places a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff and a [HP Burn] debuff on the target for 2 turns. If this attack deals damage equal to 50% or more of the target''s MAX HP, places a [Stun] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. The effects of this skill are irresistible if this Champion is under a [Veil] buff.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('db839513-9cb3-42a7-8a0b-2463d4785350','C000688-A3','A3',null,'Warrior''s Resolve','Removes all debuffs from this Champion, then heals this Champion by 50% of their MAX HP and fills their Turn Meter by 50%. Also places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff, a 15% [Shatter] buff, and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. [Passive Effect] Prevents this Champion from being killed while these buffs are active, leaving them with 1 HP instead.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('db839513-9cb3-42a7-8a0b-2463d4785350','C000688-P','Passive',null,'Assassin''s Cunning','Whenever an enemy''s HP drops below 25% after receiving damage from an Assassin ally''s skill, deals bonus damage to that enemy. The bonus damage is proportional to this Champion''s ATK.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('db839513-9cb3-42a7-8a0b-2463d4785350','C000688-A5','A5',null,'Combat Prowess','When attacking, increases this Champion''s ATK by 50% of the target''s DEF. When attacked, increases this Champion''s DEF by 50% of the attacker''s ATK.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('abbe86fa-5ffb-4260-97a2-0c850a5278a4','C000689-A1','A1',null,'Timbermaker','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, removes 1 random buff from the target. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Shield] buff. Places a [Block Revive] debuff if this attack kills an enemy. Increases the value of any [Shield] buffs on this Champion by 30% of damage dealt. Cannot increase by more than 10,000.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('abbe86fa-5ffb-4260-97a2-0c850a5278a4','C000689-A2','A2',null,'Barkbreaker','Attacks all enemies. Ignores a percentage of each target’s DEF equal to 50% of the difference between this Champion’s MAX HP and any [Shield]s on them. Also destroys each target''s MAX HP by 20% of the damage inflicted (stacks up to 50%). This effect will ignore any [Shield] buffs.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('abbe86fa-5ffb-4260-97a2-0c850a5278a4','C000689-A3','A3',null,'Hardy Soul','Places a [Shield] buff proportional to this Champion''s DEF and a 25% [Strengthen] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 2 turns.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
