  ('4ff3953d-6213-4f49-b9e7-b746ec939010','C000690-A2','A2',null,'Brand of Damnation','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore [Shield] and [Unkillable] buffs, as well as 25% of the target''s DEF. Enemies killed by this skill cannot be revived. If this attack kills an enemy, instantly activates the [Infernal Eruption] skill. If this attack does not kill an enemy, fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 50%.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
