  ('285ccf18-77b5-4731-982a-34961e800ea7','C000759-A3','A3',null,'Moonbloom''s Blessing','Revives all dead allies with 50% HP and 50% Turn Meter. If Solanar the Gleaming is on the same team and is dead, revives him with 100% Turn Meter instead. Places a [Shield] buff on all allies equal to 30% of this Champion''s MAX HP for 2 turns.','6 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('285ccf18-77b5-4731-982a-34961e800ea7','C000759-A4','A4',null,'Scholar Of Shadows [P]','All Turn Meter fill effects used by enemies are 30% less effective. If Solanar the Gleaming is on the same team, fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 30% of the enemy’s Turn Meter fill effect. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This skill will not activate on duplicate copies of this Champion, if this particular Champion is dead. Only counts Turn Meter fill effects from skills.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('1672a0e0-a46d-4d7e-b17c-f5ed3e6c3a6f','C000761-A1','A1',null,'Sting of Gungnir','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 50% chance of placing a [Berserk] debuff for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be placed on Bosses.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
