  ('c372b462-30bf-495b-b5ab-c5ffc90a63e8','C000768-P','Passive',null,'Master of Games [P]','This Champion is immune to [Stun], [HP Burn], and [Petrification] debuffs. Whenever an enemy attacks this Champion, has a 100% chance of placing a [HP Burn] debuff on that enemy for 2 turns. The chance decreases to 50% if this Champion is under a [Decrease DEF] debuff. Occurs once per enemy skill. Whenever an enemy attacks this Champion, also has a 50% chance of placing a [Petrification] debuff on that enemy for 1 turn. The chance decreases to 25% if this Champion is under a [Decrease DEF] debuff. Occurs once per enemy skill.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
