  ('9d87987f-60d4-4da4-bc9a-bf38b38961f2','C000770-P','Passive','base','Vengeful Quest','Increases this Champion''s DEF by 3% (stacks up to 30%) and MAX HP by 5% (stacks up to 50%) for each [Stun] debuff successfully landed by this Champion. Allies are immune to [Stun] debuffs while under a [Shield] buff placed by this Champion''s Good Shepherd skill.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
