  ('c941ea7e-5919-467d-b7b2-5a95da436d5b','C000486-A3','A3',null,'Unshakable Valor','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore 30% of the target’s DEF. Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 30% [Increase C. DMG] buff on this Champion for 2 turns if this attack kills an enemy. These buffs cannot be removed.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
