  ('00561451-3986-4adf-b3fb-78e56e09f5d5','C000819-A2','A2',null,'Polar Protection','Attacks all enemies. Will ignore 30% of each target''s DEF if Lady Noelle is on the same team. Places a 25% [Strengthen] buff and a [Shield] buff on all allies for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is equal to 30% of the damage inflicted.','4','3',null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('00561451-3986-4adf-b3fb-78e56e09f5d5','C000819-A3','A3',null,'Goodwill','Places an [Unkillable] buff and a 15% [Continuous Heal] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. If Lady Noelle is on the same team, also places a [Taunt] buff on this Champion for 2 turns.','6','4',null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('00561451-3986-4adf-b3fb-78e56e09f5d5','C000819-A4','A4',null,'Winter''s Warden [P]','Enemy Ignore DEF effects used against allies under [Shield] buffs are decreased by 30%. Enemy Ignore DEF effects used against Lady Noelle while she''s under a [Shield] buff are decreased by 60%.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
