  ('8726c713-dff4-497b-955a-bd11e0d12790','C000821-A2','A2',null,'Skull Comet','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 75% chance of placing a [Petrification] debuff on the target for 1 turn. Also has a 75% chance to place a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff and a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff on the target for 2 turns.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
