  ('9f835dbc-9f9b-41bf-b67a-ff2dffdba335','C000822-P','Passive','base','Halfspawn','Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 10% when attacking targets without a [Hex] debuff. Will ignore 15% of a target''s DEF when they are under a [Hex] debuff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
