  ('c67dbcad-af36-49ef-90b7-67c9618a3745','C000500-A4','A4',null,'Heir Of The Gorgoa [P]','Allies deal 10% more damage to enemies under debuffs placed by this Champion. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This skill will not activate on duplicate copies of this Champion, if this particular Champion is dead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('b6106249-f2b4-4fc6-a478-d72b4d7bc28c','C000829-A1','A1','base','Fulminant Rupture','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 75% chance of placing a [Provoke] debuff and an [Enfeeble] debuff on the target for 1 turn. Also has a 25% chance that these debuffs cannot be resisted. If each enemy has a number of buffs that is equal to or less than this Champion''s, attacks all enemies instead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('b6106249-f2b4-4fc6-a478-d72b4d7bc28c','C000829-A2','A2','base','Eye of the Storm','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff and 1 [Stormcall] stack on all allies. This attack is always critical if the number of buffs on the target is equal to or less than this Champion''s. Will ignore [Stone Skin] buff and 50% of the target''s DEF if this number of buffs on the target is equal to or less than this Champion''s. If this attack kills the target, decreases the Turn Meters of all other enemies by an amount equal to the Turn Meter that the target had.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('b6106249-f2b4-4fc6-a478-d72b4d7bc28c','C000829-A3','A3','base','Sky-Father''s Boon','Places a 30% [Increase C.RATE] buff, a [Block Damage] buff, and a [Counterattack] buff on a target ally for 2 turns. Fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 25%.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('b6106249-f2b4-4fc6-a478-d72b4d7bc28c','C000829-P','Passive','base','Boltmaster','Whenever an ally under a [Stormcall] stack placed by this Champion lands a critical hit, this Champion deals additional pure damage to the target. If the target is not a Boss or a minion, the pure damage dealt is equal to 2% of the target''s MAX HP for each buff on this Champion (stacks up to 10%). If the target is a Boss or a minion, the pure damage dealt is equal to 3% of the target''s MAX HP. This damage cannot be critical. Occurs once per skill and once per target. Does not count as an extra hit. This pure damage ignores [Shield], [Block Damage], and [Strengthen] buffs. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('ab825a40-6c22-4d40-ac9b-bea7972799d9','C000830-A1','A1','base','Doubleslash','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 35% chance of placing a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn. When counterattacking, the chance increases to 50%.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('ab825a40-6c22-4d40-ac9b-bea7972799d9','C000830-A2','A2','base','Hindrance','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, has a 75% chance of decreasing the duration of all enemy buffs by 1 turn. Has a 75% chance of placing a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('ab825a40-6c22-4d40-ac9b-bea7972799d9','C000830-A3','A3','base','Flawless Strategem','Places a 50% [Ally Protection] buff on all allies except this Champion for 2 turns, and places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Then, places a [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s DEF.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('ab825a40-6c22-4d40-ac9b-bea7972799d9','C000830-P','Passive','base','Protect The Troops','Whenever this Champion is attacked, heals themselves by 1% for each 500 DEF this Champion has. Heals all other allies under [Ally Protection] buffs placed by this Champion by 30% of this skill''s initial heal.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('b357ac41-373e-452d-8793-35231845f994','C000501-A1','A1',null,'Lotus Kiss','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 50% chance of placing a 5% [Poison] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('b357ac41-373e-452d-8793-35231845f994','C000501-A2','A2',null,'Sapping Scythes','Attacks 1 enemy. Places a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. Also places a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns if the target is under a [Poison] debuff.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('b357ac41-373e-452d-8793-35231845f994','C000501-A3','A3',null,'Shadow Dance','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('016723a2-158b-4e04-9d6a-46b2f371a9b7','C000831-A1','A1','base','Volcanic Rend','Attacks 1 enemy. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 15%. Also fills the Turn Meters of all allies, except this Champion, by 10%, when attacking a target under [HP Burn] debuff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('016723a2-158b-4e04-9d6a-46b2f371a9b7','C000831-A2','A2','base','Blazing Barrier','Places a [HP Burn] debuff on all enemies for 3 turns, and instantly activates any [HP Burn] debuffs on all enemies. Then places a [Shield] buff on all allies for 2 turns equal to the damage inflicted by the [HP Burn] activation. The value of the [Shield] buff cannot exceed 25,000 HP.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('016723a2-158b-4e04-9d6a-46b2f371a9b7','C000831-A3','A3','base','Rise From Ash','Revives all dead allies with 50% HP and 40% Turn Meter. Grants an Extra Turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('016723a2-158b-4e04-9d6a-46b2f371a9b7','C000831-P','Passive','base','Pyroclastic Boon','Fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 5% for each [HP Burn] debuff placed. Whenever a [HP Burn] debuff is activated, heals all allies by 5% of their MAX HP. Whenever a [HP Burn] debuff is activated on Skavag, Tainted Skavag, Spiderlings, or Tainted Spiderlings, heals all allies by 1% of their MAX HP. Whenever a [HP Burn] debuff is removed from an enemy, places a 50% [Decrease RES] debuff on that enemy for 1 turn. Whenever an ally is killed by an enemy under a [HP Burn] debuff, fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 20%. Increases this Champion''s SPD by 7 for each active [HP Burn] debuff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('89293b1f-6b1c-4b40-b793-a7e662d53b42','C000832-A1','A1',null,'Gotcha!','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 25% chance of placing a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn. The chance increases to 50% if the target has any buffs.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('89293b1f-6b1c-4b40-b793-a7e662d53b42','C000832-A2','A2',null,'Staff of Wonder','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore 50% of the target’s DEF. Will attack all remaining enemies with any surplus damage if the target is killed. This attack will also ignore 50% of the target’s DEF. This attack cannot be critical. If the initial target survives, places a [Sheep] debuff on them for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be blocked.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('89293b1f-6b1c-4b40-b793-a7e662d53b42','C000832-A3','A3',null,'Now You See Us','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, steals all buffs from all enemies and then places a [Block Buffs] debuff on them for 2 turns.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('89293b1f-6b1c-4b40-b793-a7e662d53b42','C000832-A4','A4',null,'Unbeatable Wukong [P]','Revives this Champion with 100% HP and 100% Turn Meter 3 turns after they were killed.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('3f8ff348-1071-47a5-91d8-4cf8dc16f440','C000260-A1','A1','base','Restorative Slash','Attacks 1 enemy. Places an extra hit if the target is under a [Decrease DEF] debuff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('3f8ff348-1071-47a5-91d8-4cf8dc16f440','C000260-A2','A2','base','Sunken Swords','Attacks all enemies. Has a 50% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns. The chance increases by 5% for each alive ally.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('3f8ff348-1071-47a5-91d8-4cf8dc16f440','C000260-A3','A3','base','Defender of Agaris','Attacks 1 enemy. Heals this Champion by 20% of the damage inflicted. Heals this Champion by 30% instead if the target is under a [Decrease DEF] debuff. Destroys the target''s MAX HP by 20% of the damage inflicted. Destroys the target''s MAX HP by 30% instead if the target is under a [Decrease DEF] debuff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('bac4bb44-8617-4871-815f-b1459ee607fe','C000834-A1','A1',null,'Skill 1','Attacks twice, transferring a random Debuff from herself to a target.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('bac4bb44-8617-4871-815f-b1459ee607fe','C000834-A2','A2',null,'Skill 2','Deals a huge amount of damage, increasing damage by 10% for each debuff on targets. If a target is killed, resets the cooldown of Crack Shot (A3).',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('bac4bb44-8617-4871-815f-b1459ee607fe','C000834-A3','A3',null,'Crack Shot','Targets an enemy to take them out first. Grants an extra turn if the target is killed.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
