  ('b265d43d-34a3-41d9-aa6b-f71790356276','C000835-A1','A1','base','Exemplar of Rage','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has an extra 10% chance of inflicting a critical hit. Each hit also has a 40% chance of increasing the duration of any [HP Burn] debuffs on the target.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('b265d43d-34a3-41d9-aa6b-f71790356276','C000835-A2','A2','base','Bloodshed Tempest','Attacks 4 times at random. Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on this Champion for 3 turns before attacking. Each hit has an extra 10% chance of inflicting a critical hit. Each hit also has a 75% chance of instantly activating any [HP Burn] debuffs on each target and decreasing the duration of those [HP Burn] debuffs by 1 turn. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 30% if 3 or more [HP Burn] debuffs are activated during the attack.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('b265d43d-34a3-41d9-aa6b-f71790356276','C000835-A3','A3','base','Unreasoning Outburst','Attacks all enemies. Has an extra 10% chance of inflicting a critical hit. Has a 75% chance of placing [HP Burn] and [Block Buffs] debuffs for 2 turns. Also places a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff on targets whose Turn Meter is higher than 50%.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('b265d43d-34a3-41d9-aa6b-f71790356276','C000835-P','Passive','base','Laugh at Danger','Whenever this Champion receives a [Fear], [True Fear], [Freeze], [Provoke], [Sleep], [Stun] or [Petrification] debuff, instantly removes it. Then fully heals this Champion, and grants an extra turn.','4 turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('00f424e6-9c2f-42ac-9e93-a0b7122adb9d','C000836-A1','A1','base','Exemplar of Skill','Attacks all enemies. Has a 50% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be resisted.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('00f424e6-9c2f-42ac-9e93-a0b7122adb9d','C000836-A2','A2','base','Putrescene','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing three 5% [Poison] debuffs for 2 turns. These debuffs cannot be resisted. Also increases the duration of all enemy debuffs by 1 turn. This effect cannot be resisted.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('00f424e6-9c2f-42ac-9e93-a0b7122adb9d','C000836-A3','A3','base','Arcane Havoc','Attacks all enemies. Places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns before attacking. Also has a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease RES] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be resisted. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 10% for each [Decrease RES] debuff placed by this skill.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('00f424e6-9c2f-42ac-9e93-a0b7122adb9d','C000836-P','Passive','base','Degrade','Decreases each target''s ACC, C.RATE, and C.DMG by 3% for each [Poison] debuff on them. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('12fe8718-e769-40a4-bb92-3f2c69a51324','C000838-A1','A1',null,'A1','Swarmspeaker can steal one buff from an enemy or rely on allies to remove them, enabling him to deal 50% more damage on his next attack.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives')
