values
  ('12fe8718-e769-40a4-bb92-3f2c69a51324','C000838-A2','A2',null,'Ravening Multitude','This single target attack grants him an extra turn if it kills an enemy, or, if the target survives, it places an additional hit on all enemies.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('12fe8718-e769-40a4-bb92-3f2c69a51324','C000838-P','Passive',null,'A3','A double hitting attack, scales its damage by 10% for each debuff placed on enemies, resetting after each use. With the full Faction Unity bonus, this skill gains a 50% chance to trigger whenever enemies attempt to place buffs, enabling further attacks. Each kill with this ability increases his ATK by 30% [up to 120%], resets its cooldown, and fills his Turn Meter, enabling him to cycle through turns faster.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('12fe8718-e769-40a4-bb92-3f2c69a51324','C000838-P2','Passive 2',null,'Swarm Conductor','Will ignore 12% of each target''s DEF if they have no buffs. [Dark Elves Unity] 1 Faction Ally: Allies receive 15% less damage from enemies that have any buffs. Allies receive 30% less damage from enemies that have no buffs. 2 Faction Ally: When this Champion or an ally removes or steals a buff from an enemy, this Champion''s next skill will deal 50% more damage. 3 Faction Ally: At the start of each round, places a [Block Buffs] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be resisted.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('f69c408d-e48a-4439-b15b-645403c22b70','C000839-A1','A1','base','Fleshcleaver','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 80% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff and a [Pain Link] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('f69c408d-e48a-4439-b15b-645403c22b70','C000839-A2','A2','base','Brutal Decapitator','Attacks all enemies 2 times. The first hit has a 75% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns. The second hit has a 75% chance of placing a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('f69c408d-e48a-4439-b15b-645403c22b70','C000839-A3','A3','base','Bond of the Enslaved','Places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a 50% [Ally Protection] buff on all allies except this Champion for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
