  ('dc1ffa97-e0c3-4919-ad89-c0293d28d0c1','C000504-A1','A1',null,'Seeker Bolts','Attacks 2 times at random. Heals all allies by 3% of this Champion''s HP with each hit on targets under [Decrease SPD] debuffs.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
