  ('2b57245a-5510-4c26-934f-a4dafce80c65','C000840-A3','A3',null,'Quell The Darkness','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Has a 75% chance of decreasing the duration of all enemy buffs by 2 turns. Also has a 75% chance of increasing the cooldowns of all enemy skills by 2 turns.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('2b57245a-5510-4c26-934f-a4dafce80c65','C000840-P','Passive',null,'Evil Wanes Before Her [P]','Increases all allies’ Turn Meters by 2% whenever a [Poison] debuff is activated on an enemy. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This skill will not activate on duplicate copies of this Champion, if this particular Champion is dead. Decreases enemies’ C. RATE by 5% and C. DMG by 10% for each [Poison] debuff on them. This effect does not work against Bosses.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
  ('93ce1922-3ef0-4fff-aafb-9ae5c48032d2','C000841-A1','A1',null,'Attack 1','Places a [Decrease ATK] debuff on a 50% chance. Increases all allies'' Turn Meters by 5% per critical hit (10% total per attack).',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','web-sourced 2026-07-09; user-approved for seeding; slot positional — verify passives'),
