  ('75390a65-4b29-4c13-a906-d0990ca28ea0','C000842-A3','A3','base','Purgation Blade','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Before attacking, removes all debuffs from this Champion and steals all buffs from the target enemy. Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 30% [Increase C.DMG] buff on this Champion for 2 turns if this attack kills an enemy. These buffs cannot be removed.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
