  ('3ad705d5-3b32-4f36-9997-9a7e98b05bed','C000002-Passive','Passive','base','Battle Revelry [P]','Each time this Champion hits an enemy under a [Leech] debuff, increases this Champion''s DEF and HP by 5% (stacks up to 50%). When attacked by enemies whose ATK is higher than or equal to their DEF, has a 100% chance to place a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns. When attacked by enemies whose DEF is higher than their ATK, has a 100% chance to place a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns instead. When attacked by enemies under a [Leech] debuff, has a 50% chance to place a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3ad705d5-3b32-4f36-9997-9a7e98b05bed','C000002-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Blade Axel','Attacks 1 enemy. Places a [Block Buffs] debuff for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be resisted if the target''s HP is lower than this Champion''s.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3ad705d5-3b32-4f36-9997-9a7e98b05bed','C000002-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Frenzied Execution','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore [Stone Skin] buffs. The damage inflicted by this skill increases by 50% if the target''s HP is lower than this Champion''s. Resets the cooldown of this skill if the target is killed.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3ad705d5-3b32-4f36-9997-9a7e98b05bed','C000002-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Soul Separator','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, places a 30% [Increase C.DMG] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Steals 50% of the target''s Turn Meter. Steals 100% Turn Meter instead if the target''s HP is lower than this Champion''s. Destroys the target''s HP by 25%. Destroys 50% HP if the target''s HP is lower than this Champion''s.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3ad705d5-3b32-4f36-9997-9a7e98b05bed','C000002-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3ad705d5-3b32-4f36-9997-9a7e98b05bed','C000002-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Rage Nexus [P]','Will ignore 15% of a target''s DEF if the target''s HP is lower than this Champion''s. Will also ignore 15% of the target''s DEF if the target is under a [Leech] debuff. Every third skill this Champion uses will attack all enemies instead. This Champion joins every third attacking skill used by allies. This Champion will use their default skill when joining in that skill.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('46bbb3bb-6b80-4364-9083-27b32649599d','C000003-A1','A1','base','Pride''s Bite','Attacks 1 enemy. Places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff on all allies for 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('46bbb3bb-6b80-4364-9083-27b32649599d','C000003-A2','A2','base','Radiant Claw','Attacks all enemies. Increases the duration of all ally buffs by 1 turn. Also heals all allies by 4% of their MAX HP for every buff on them that had its duration increased.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('46bbb3bb-6b80-4364-9083-27b32649599d','C000003-A3','A3','base','Rock of Werinbur','Places a 50% [Increase RES] buff, a 25% [Strengthen] buff, and a 15% [Continuous Heal] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Places an additional 15% [Continuous Heal] buff on all allies with less than 50% HP for 2 turns. Also fills the Turn Meter of all allies by 15%.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('46bbb3bb-6b80-4364-9083-27b32649599d','C000003-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('46bbb3bb-6b80-4364-9083-27b32649599d','C000003-Passive','Passive','base','Knights of the Wild [P]','Increases each ally''s RES by 10 for each buff on all allies. Critical hits inflicted by allies fill the Turn Meters of all allies by 5%. Occurs once per skill. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This skill will not activate on duplicate copies of this Champion, if this particular Champion is dead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('5406b5c2-2a6c-42da-81fd-c15c3eeb6be1','C000004-A1','A1','base','Blink Cut','Attacks 1 enemy. Places a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns. Also places a [Perfect Veil] buff on this Champion for 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('5406b5c2-2a6c-42da-81fd-c15c3eeb6be1','C000004-A2','A2','base','Umbral Stingers','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Will ignore 25% of a target''s DEF if they are not under a [HP Burn] debuff. Will ignore 50% of a target''s DEF if they are under a [HP Burn] debuff. Then, increases the duration of all enemy debuffs by 1 turn.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('5406b5c2-2a6c-42da-81fd-c15c3eeb6be1','C000004-A3','A3','base','Blisterbug Horde','Attacks all enemies. Damage increases by 25% against targets under any debuffs. Instantly activates one tick of all [HP Burn] debuffs on all enemies. If an enemy is not under any [HP Burn] debuffs, place a [HP Burn] debuff on them for 2 turns.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('5406b5c2-2a6c-42da-81fd-c15c3eeb6be1','C000004-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('5406b5c2-2a6c-42da-81fd-c15c3eeb6be1','C000004-Passive','Passive','base','Fleshsearer [P]','Each time this Champion places a [HP Burn] debuff, decreases the target''s DEF by 3% (stacks up to 30%). For each [HP Burn] debuff on the enemy team, increase this Champion''s C.DMG by 10% (stacks up to 100%). Whenever an enemy [HP Burn] debuff activates, increase this Champion''s ATK by 5% (stacks up to 50%). Resets each Round.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-A1','A1','base','Mesmeric Fangs','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit decreases the target''s Turn Meter by 5%. Each hit decreases the target''s Turn Meter by an additional 5% if the target is under any debuffs placed by this Champion.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-A2','A2','base','Moon-Spider Maw','Attacks all enemies. Decreases the Turn Meters of all enemies by 50%. Decreases the Turn Meters of all enemies by 100% instead if this skill is used on an Extra Turn or Instant Turn. Places a [True Fear] debuff for 1 turn. Places a [True Fear] debuff for 2 turns instead against enemies whose Turn Meter is fully decreased by this skill and Bosses.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-A3','A3','base','Dark Trance','Removes all buffs from all enemies. Places a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff and a [Block Active Skills] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Grants an Extra Turn if 8 or more debuffs were placed by this skill.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-Passive','Passive','base','Spiderscuttle [P]','Increases this Champion''s SPD by 4 for each debuff placed by this Champion and by 2 for each debuff resisted when this Champion attempts to place debuffs (stacks up to 100). Only counts debuffs placed by this Champion''s skills.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Astral Ravage','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 5% for each critical hit. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by an additional 5% for each critical hit, if the target is under a [Block Active Skills] debuff or a [Decrease DEF] debuff. If this attack kills an enemy, grants an Extra Turn instead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Deaththread Spin','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. Will always use this skill instead of the default skill when counterattacking. This skill cannot be blocked by [Block Active Skills] debuffs. Will ignore [Shield] and [Block Damage] buffs. Additionally ignores [Unkillable] buffs if the target is under a [Block Active Skills] debuff or a [Decrease DEF] debuff. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 15% for each critical hit.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Gossamer Execution','Attacks 1 enemy 4 times. Each hit will ignore 15% of the target''s DEF. Each hit will ignore 30% DEF instead if the target is under a [Block Active Skills] debuff or a [Decrease DEF] debuff. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 20% for each critical hit. Then places a [Perfect Veil] buff on this Champion for 2 turns.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion | Metamorph CD needs Index verification'),
  ('c815fd25-fe29-4295-8848-d75a1cbb4bc6','C000005-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Great Web Mistress [P]','This Champion is immune to [Stun], [Sleep], [Fear], [True Fear], [Provoke], [Freeze], and [Petrification] debuffs while under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff. This Champion also cannot receive critical hits while under a [Veil] or [Perfect Veil] buff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('68010857-61fc-4dc1-8280-c7b53ac8350f','C000006-A1','A1','base','Bladegale','Attacks all enemies. Has a 40% chance of placing a [Block Active Skills] debuff for 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
