  ('68010857-61fc-4dc1-8280-c7b53ac8350f','C000006-A3','A3','base','Harmonious Whisper','Fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 30% and places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
