  ('68010857-61fc-4dc1-8280-c7b53ac8350f','C000006-Passive','Passive','base','Stonethorn''s Embrace [P]','Has a 30% chance of placing a [Petrification] debuff on an attacker for 1 turn, whenever an ally is attacked while under a [Revive On Death] buff placed by this Champion.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
