  ('68010857-61fc-4dc1-8280-c7b53ac8350f','C000006-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Roar of the Mistwood','Places two 15% [Continuous Heal] buffs on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a [Taunt] buff on this Champion for 2 turns, as well as a [Stone Skin] buff for 1 turn.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
