  ('c0d73b3a-8236-4e9a-afe2-bb4c762b736e','C000007-Passive','Passive','base','Will Of The Tundra [P]','[Passive Effect] Enemies under a [Deathbrand] debuff receive 20% more damage and inflict 20% less damage. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This skill will not activate on duplicate copies of this Champion, if this particular Champion is dead. This Champion is immune to [Freeze], [Stun], and [Provoke] debuffs. [Active Effect] Whenever this Champion is killed, revives them with 50% HP, 100% Turn Meter, and places a [Block Damage] buff on them for 1 turn.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-A1','A1','base','Ignition Arc','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. Each hit has a 50% chance of increasing the duration of all debuffs on the target by 1 turn. Each hit has a 100% chance to increase the duration of a [HP Burn] debuff on the target by 1 turn instead, if the initial chance does not activate.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-A2','A2','base','Pyroclast Storm','Attacks all enemies. Instantly activates all [HP Burn] debuffs on all enemies and allies. Whenever a [HP Burn] debuff is activated on an enemy by this skill, decreases their RES by 10 (stacks up to 100). Whenever a [HP Burn] debuff is activated on an ally by this skill, increases their RES by 10 (stacks up to 100). Also fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 5% for each [HP Burn] debuff activated on enemies.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-A3','A3','base','Wreathed In Flame','Places a 25% [Weaken] debuff and a [HP Burn] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Also places a [HP Burn] debuff on all allies for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be blocked or resisted. Then fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 30%.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-Passive','Passive','base','By Fire Be Healed [P]','Each [HP Burn] debuff placed by this Champion while in their Base Form increases their MAX HP and DEF by 5% (stacks up to 25% across both Forms and will not reset). [HP Burn] debuffs placed on allies heal them instead of damaging them. Allies deal 3% more damage for each active [HP Burn] debuff. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Thunderstar','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Has a 25% chance of repeating each hit. Each hit also places a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Magma Geyser','Attacks 1 enemy. Applies a [Debuff Spread] effect, taking all debuffs from the target and placing them on all enemies. Then, repeats the attack on all enemies. Increases the duration of all debuffs on all enemies by 1 turn. Both attacks will ignore 20% of each target''s DEF.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Cataclysm Smash','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff and a 30% [Increase C. DMG] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Places a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn. If the target of this skill is a Boss, places a [Provoke] debuff for 2 turns instead. This attack cannot be a weak hit when hitting enemies under a [HP Burn] debuff.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('bcaef84c-eaf3-4894-97ae-a1cc10dab6ea','C000008-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','By Fire Be Broken [P]','Each [HP Burn] debuff placed by this Champion''s Base Form increases this Champion''s MAX HP and DEF by 5% (stacks up to 25% across both Forms and will not reset). All of this Champion''s skills will ignore 20% of the enemy''s DEF if they are under a [HP Burn] debuff. [HP Burn] debuffs placed on allies heal them instead of damaging them.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-A1','A1','base','Hatespine','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Will repeat the attack against the enemy with the highest Turn Meter if the initial target is under a [Leech] debuff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-A2','A2','base','Crimson Steel','Attacks all enemies. Places a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn, and decreases the Turn Meters of all enemies by 50%. These effects cannot be resisted by targets whose ATK is lower than this Champion''s.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-A3','A3','base','Hemaelstrom','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, removes all buffs from enemies. This effect cannot be resisted by targets whose ATK is lower than this Champion''s. Places a [Leech] debuff and a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. These debuffs cannot be resisted by targets whose ATK is lower than this Champion''s.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-A4','A4','base','Metamorph [P]','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form whenever this Champion is revived by a skill, effect, or [Revive On Death] buff. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion | Metamorph is passive-triggered (revive condition), not manually activated'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-Passive','Passive','base','Engine of Murder [P]','Whenever an enemy has their Turn Meter filled, this Champion inflicts pure damage on that enemy equal to 3% of their MAX HP for every 10% Turn Meter filled. Will inflict 6% of their MAX HP as pure damage instead, if the enemy is under a [Leech] debuff. This damage cannot be critical and will ignore [Stone Skin], [Ally Protection], [Shield], [Strengthen], and [Fervor] buffs, [Bone Armor] stacks, and any damage modifying skills or effects. If the enemy is a Boss, the damage cannot exceed 50,000 HP per hit. Whenever an enemy has their Turn Meter filled, also destroys their SPD by 3 for every 10% Turn Meter filled (stacks up to 100). Will destroy 6 SPD for every 10% Turn Meter filled instead, if the enemy is under a [Leech] debuff. This effect does not work against Bosses. Revives this Champion with 100% HP every 2 turns if at least one ally is alive. Once per Round, instantly revives this Champion with 100% HP if all allies are dead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Tempest of Swords','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Will ignore 10% of the target''s DEF. Will ignore 20% of the target''s DEF instead if the target''s ATK is lower than this Champion''s. The damage inflicted by this skill increases by 5% for each debuff on the target.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Goading Roar','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Will ignore 50% of the target''s DEF. Will ignore 100% of the target''s DEF instead if the target''s ATK is lower than this Champion''s. Will also ignore [Block Damage] and [Unkillable] buffs if the target is under a [Heal Reduction] debuff. If this skill kills an enemy, heals this Champion by 100% of their MAX HP, and will repeat the attack on a random target under a [Fear] or [True Fear] debuff. Occurs once per skill.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Glacial Rupture','Attacks all enemies. Places a 100% [Heal Reduction] debuff and a [True Fear] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Will ignore [Block Debuffs] buffs. These debuffs cannot be resisted by targets whose ATK is lower than this Champion''s. Will also ignore 20% of each target''s DEF if the target''s ATK is lower than this Champion''s.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('1ef6e374-67e7-49da-b9ff-210d78a7fe47','C000909-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Bear-Heart [P]','Heals this Champion by 1% of their MAX HP for every 1% of Turn Meter filled by enemies. Will heal this Champion by 2% of their MAX HP for every 1% of Turn Meter filled by enemies instead, if this Champion''s ATK is higher than the enemy''s. Increases this Champion''s SPD by 3 for every 1% of Turn Meter filled by enemies (stacks up to 100). Will increase this Champion''s SPD by 6 for every 1% of Turn Meter filled by enemies instead, if this Champion''s ATK is higher than the enemy''s.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3aa9cc69-dd9e-4100-b75a-951e34497761','C000910-A1','A1','base','Eruptive Blow','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit ignores 15% of the target''s DEF. Ignores 30% of the target''s DEF instead if this Champion is under a [Magma Shield] buff. Will attack all remaining enemies with any surplus damage if the initial target is killed.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3aa9cc69-dd9e-4100-b75a-951e34497761','C000910-A2','A2','base','Breaker Of Metals','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit ignores 25% of the target''s DEF. Ignores 50% of the target''s DEF instead if this Champion is under a [Magma Shield] buff. Will also deal double damage if the target is under a [Shield] buff. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 50% and places a [Magma Shield] buff equal to 200% of this Champion''s ATK on this Champion for 1 turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3aa9cc69-dd9e-4100-b75a-951e34497761','C000910-A3','A3','base','In Magma Clad','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit ignores 35% of the target''s DEF. Will also deal double damage and ignore [Unkillable] and [Block Damage] buffs if this Champion is under a [Magma Shield] buff. Places a [Magma Shield] buff equal to 300% of this Champion''s ATK on all allies for 2 turns and grants this Champion an Extra Turn if this attack kills the target.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3aa9cc69-dd9e-4100-b75a-951e34497761','C000910-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('3aa9cc69-dd9e-4100-b75a-951e34497761','C000910-Passive','Passive','base','Furnace-Shell [P]','At the start of each Round and whenever this Champion is revived, places a [Magma Shield] buff equal to 300% of this Champion''s ATK on this Champion for 1 turn. This Champion receives 30% less damage from enemies when under a [Magma Shield] buff. Heals this Champion by 50% of their MAX HP whenever a [Magma Shield] buff on them expires or is removed by damage.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('add0176d-4aeb-49ca-b83e-d7237c280268','C000911-A1','A1','base','Fetid Glaive','Attacks all enemies. Destroys each target''s MAX HP by 3% (stacks up to 30%). Also increases the duration of 1 random debuff on all enemies by 1 turn. This effect cannot be resisted if enemies have any [Necrosis] stacks.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('add0176d-4aeb-49ca-b83e-d7237c280268','C000911-A2','A2','base','Voidstare','Places a [True Fear] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn, and a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. These effects cannot be resisted if enemies have any [Necrosis] stacks. Then grants an Extra Turn.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('add0176d-4aeb-49ca-b83e-d7237c280268','C000911-A3','A3','base','The Unmaking','Attacks all enemies. Removes any [Stone Skin] buffs and replaces them with [True Fear] debuffs. [Block Debuffs] buffs will be replaced with [Block Buffs] debuffs. Also removes any buffs positively affecting stats, and replaces them with their mirrored debuff equivalent, such as [Increase ATK] being replaced with [Decrease ATK]. Buffs such as [Continuous Heal] and [Strengthen] will be replaced with [Heal Reduction] and [Weaken] debuffs respectively. The mirrored debuffs will have the same duration as the buffs before they were replaced. Then steals 5% of each target''s Turn Meter for each buff converted into a debuff by this skill. Also decreases the Turn Meters of all enemies by 20%. These effects cannot be resisted if enemies have any [Necrosis] stacks.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('add0176d-4aeb-49ca-b83e-d7237c280268','C000911-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('add0176d-4aeb-49ca-b83e-d7237c280268','C000911-Passive','Passive','base','Wrongful Existence [P]','Whenever an enemy is killed, places one [Necrosis] stack on all other enemies. [Necrosis] stacks cannot be resisted or blocked. [Necrosis] stacks can only be removed by reviving dead allies. This effect does not work against Bosses and their minions. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, this effect will only activate once. At the start and the end of this Champion''s turn, instantly activates any [Necrosis] stacks on all enemies.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('add0176d-4aeb-49ca-b83e-d7237c280268','C000911-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Alternate A1','Attacks targets affected by [Necrosis] twice, with a chance to [Block Revive].',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('add0176d-4aeb-49ca-b83e-d7237c280268','C000911-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Alternate A2','Deals double damage if this Champion has more Accuracy than the target, or ignores 50% Defence if this Champion has less Accuracy than the target.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('add0176d-4aeb-49ca-b83e-d7237c280268','C000911-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Alternate A3','Grants 10% permanent Ignore Defence (stacks up to 50%). Fully heals this Champion and restores destroyed HP against bosses, or swaps HP with an enemy.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('add0176d-4aeb-49ca-b83e-d7237c280268','C000911-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Alternate Passive','Reflects 50% of damage taken and surplus damage when killed. Cheats death by putting this Champion on 1 HP and applying [Revive on Death]. Reflect includes excessive damage.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-A1','A1','base','Wing Clip','Attacks 1 enemy. Places a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns. When counterattacking, the damage inflicted by this skill is based on this Champion''s DEF and the enemy''s MAX HP.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-A2','A2','base','Cutting Jibe','Attacks all enemies. Places a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn. If the target is a Boss, places a [Provoke] debuff for 2 turns instead. Also places an [Unkillable] buff on this Champion for 1 turn and a [Counterattack] buff on them for 2 turns.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-A3','A3','base','Bloodcrest''s Call','Fully restores all allies'' destroyed MAX HP. Also places a [Revive On Death] buff and a 60% [Increase DEF] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Then, grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-Passive','Passive','base','Rule the Roost [P]','Reflects 50% of the damage this Champion receives back to the attacker. If the attacker is a Boss, reflects 100% of the damage this Champion receives. Also heals this Champion by 50% of the damage received.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Fulminous Screech','Attacks 1 enemy. Places an extra hit on all enemies under [Decrease DEF] debuffs.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Sundered Sky','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns. This effect cannot be resisted. Damage increases by 10% for each enemy under a [Decrease DEF] debuff. Also steals 20% of the Turn Meter from each enemy.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Sonic Torture','Attacks all enemies. Will ignore 20% of each target''s DEF if they have no buffs. Ignores [Block Damage] buffs. Damage increases by 15% for each buff on each target. Decreases the duration of all enemy buffs by 2 turns.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('59b72f01-3c50-4ae7-b7a2-638680a12d49','C000914-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Unholy Experiment [P]','Immune to [Stun], [Freeze], [Sleep], [Fear], [True Fear], [Provoke], [Sheep], and [Petrification] debuffs. Also randomly resets the cooldown of one of this Champion''s skills whenever they kill an enemy. Occurs once per skill.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-A1','A1','base','Foecrusher','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, removes all buffs from the target. Increases the cooldown of a random skill on the target by 2 turns, even if this attack lands as a weak hit.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-A2','A2','base','Hammerquake','Attacks all enemies. Places a [Provoke] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. This debuff will ignore [Block Debuffs] buff and can be placed even if this attack lands as a weak hit. Also places a protected [Unkillable] buff and a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 3 turns.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-A3','A3','base','Bonded by Blood','Removes all debuffs from all allies and places a 50% [Ally Protection] buff on all allies except this Champion for 2 turns. Also places a [Shield] buff on all allies equal to 30% of this Champion''s MAX HP for 2 turns. Increases the value of the [Shield] by an additional 3% of this Champion''s MAX HP per each debuff removed by this skill.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-Passive','Passive','base','Kill or Cure [P]','When attacked, decreases the duration of all buffs on the attacker by 1 turn. Occurs once per hit. Also heals all allies except this Champion by 50% of the damage taken, and heals this Champion by 25% of the damage taken, whenever this Champion is hit. Occurs once per hit.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Magma Slam','Attacks all enemies. Has a 25% chance of repeating the attack. Will ignore [Block Damage] buffs.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Calamitious Maul','Attacks all enemies. Damage of this skill increases by 10% for each buff on this Champion and on the target. Will ignore 30% of the target''s DEF. Will ignore 50% of the target''s DEF instead if this Champion has more buffs than the target.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Cornered Animal','Removes all debuffs from this Champion. Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff, a 30% [Increase C.DMG] buff, and a 30% [Increase C. RATE] buff on all allies for 3 turns. Grants an Extra Turn. [This skill unlocks when this Champion has 3 or more debuffs, or when this Champion has 50% or less HP.]','2 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('41ad2872-bfa1-4647-9724-d587e539e008','C000915-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Crimson Haze [P]','Whenever an ally attacks, this Champion has a 50% chance to team up with them and join their attack. This Champion inflicts more damage as their HP decreases (by 1% for every 1% of HP lost). This Champion receives less damage as their HP decreases (by 0.5% for every 1% of HP lost).',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-A1','A1','base','Magma Hurl','Attacks 1 enemy. Increases the duration of any [HP Burn] debuffs on the target by 1 turn. If the target is not under a [HP Burn] debuff, decreases the duration of 2 random buffs on that enemy by 1 turn instead. These effects cannot be resisted if this attack is critical. Then, attacks all enemies not under [HP Burn] debuffs, except the initial target. Decreases the duration of 2 random buffs on all enemies hit by 1 turn. This effect cannot be resisted if this attack is critical.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-A2','A2','base','Flames of Resentment','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, increases the duration of all [HP Burn] debuffs on all enemies by 1 turn, then instantly activates one tick of all [HP Burn] debuffs on all enemies. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion''s C.RATE is 100% or higher. Finally, increases the duration of all debuffs on all enemies by 1 turn, and places a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. These effects cannot be resisted if this attack is critical.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-A3','A3','base','Let Me At ''Em!','Places a 30% [Increase C.DMG] buff, a 30% [Increase C.RATE] buff and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on all allies for 3 turns. Then, grants an Extra Turn.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-Passive','Passive','base','Spark of Anger [P]','Before any Champion takes their turn in a Round, places a [HP Burn] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Occurs once per Round. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion''s C.RATE is 100% or higher. Also before the start of this Champion''s turn, has a 50% chance of placing a [HP Burn] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion''s C.RATE is 100% or higher.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Totemic Vengeance','Attacks 1 enemy. If this Champion''s HP or the initial target''s HP is equal to or lower than 50%, attacks all enemies instead. Increases the duration of 2 random debuffs on the target by 1 turn. If attacking all enemies, increases the duration of 2 random debuffs on all enemies by 1 turn instead. This effect cannot be resisted if this attack is critical.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','KABOOM!','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be resisted if the target is under a [HP Burn] debuff. Places an extra hit on enemies under [HP Burn] debuffs. Grants an Extra Turn if this attack kills an enemy.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Ungodly Fury','Places a [Pain Link] debuff on a target enemy for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be removed, resisted, or blocked. When calculating the damage inflicted by the [Pain Link] debuff, 75% of the attacker''s skill multiplier is reflected. The damage inflicted by the [Pain Link] debuff will ignore 100% of the target''s DEF. Also places a [Taunt] buff and an [Unkillable] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Finally, places a 50% [Ally Protection] buff on all allies except this Champion for 2 turns.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0b7361b7-d41e-4617-83ac-eb796521eb59','C000916-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Burning Juggernaut [P]','Will ignore 15% of a target''s DEF if this Champion''s HP or the target''s HP is equal to or greater than 50%. If this Champion''s HP or the target''s HP is less than 50%, will ignore 25% of the target''s DEF instead. Will also ignore [Block Damage] and [Shield] buffs when attacking enemies under [HP Burn] debuffs. Inflicts 20% more damage to enemies not under a [HP Burn] debuff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-A1','A1','base','Phantom Cobra','Attacks 1 enemy. Places a [Shield] buff on the ally with the lowest HP for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s ATK.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-A2','A2','base','Nest of Vipers','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a [Block Debuffs] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also decreases the duration of all buffs on all enemies by 2 turns. After attacking, places a [Block Buffs] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-A3','A3','base','The Rift''s Gaze','Fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 20%. Also decreases the Turn Meters of all enemies by 20%. Then, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 25% [Strengthen] buff on all allies for 2 turns.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-Passive','Passive','base','Reality Shift [P]','[Passive Effect] At the start of this Champion''s turn, places a [Perfect Veil] buff and a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on them for 2 turns. Also, this Champion receives 3% less damage for every 750 ATK they have (stacks up to 30%). [Active Effect] At the end of this Champion''s turn, revive a random ally with 50% HP and 50% Turn Meter. Also places a [Perfect Veil] buff on the revived ally for 2 turns.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Lambent Trident','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. The first hit increases this Champion''s ATK by 3% (stacks up to 30%). The second hit decreases 3% of the target''s ATK or DEF or destroys 3% of the target''s MAX HP, depending on their Type (stacks up to 30%). [This effect does not work against Support Type Champions.]',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Destruction Surge','Attacks all enemies. Will ignore [Shield] and [Increase DEF] buffs. Before attacking, removes all debuffs from this Champion. Increases this attack''s damage by 15% for each debuff removed. If no debuffs were removed from this Champion, increases this attack''s damage by 15% for each alive ally instead.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Flame Vulcan','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Will ignore any [Ally Protection], [Strengthen], and [Shield] buffs, as well as 30% of the target''s DEF. Before attacking, steals 50% of the target''s Turn Meter. This effect cannot be resisted.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('6989047d-12f6-4d0a-a550-4dd0a9d87833','C000917-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Overwhelming Power [P]','[Passive Effect] At the start of this Champion''s turn, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 30% [Increase C. DMG] buff on them for 2 turns. [Active Effect] Increases the cooldown of all enemy skills by 2 turns whenever this Champion kills an enemy. If this Champion kills two or more enemies in a single attack, this effect will only activate once. This effect cannot be resisted.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion | passive skill with active effect - CD 3 applies to active component only'),
  ('0ef487dc-6320-4c8b-aff6-c9159b09e9e6','C000918-A1','A1','base','Radiant Blades','Attacks all enemies. Heals all allies by 5% of their MAX HP and 5% of this Champion''s RES. Has a 50% chance of placing a random 1-turn buff on all allies.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0ef487dc-6320-4c8b-aff6-c9159b09e9e6','C000918-A2','A2','base','Luminant Shield','Removes all debuffs from all allies. Places a 2-turn 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 2-turn 60% [Increase RES] buff on all allies. Increases the Turn Meters of all allies by 15%.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0ef487dc-6320-4c8b-aff6-c9159b09e9e6','C000918-A3','A3','base','Divine Intervention','Revives a target ally with 50% HP and 100% Turn Meter. Places a 1-turn [Unkillable] buff on them. If no allies are dead, activates this Champion''s [Luminant Shield] skill instead.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0ef487dc-6320-4c8b-aff6-c9159b09e9e6','C000918-Passive','Passive','base','Lumaya''s Blessing','Increases the damage all allies inflict by 15% against enemies whose RES is lower than this Champion''s RES. Also, activates this Champion''s [Divine Intervention] skill whenever an enemy revives. Occurs once per turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('0ef487dc-6320-4c8b-aff6-c9159b09e9e6','C000918-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Blades of Vengeance','Attacks all enemies. Damage increases by 5% for each 100 RES this Champion has. When attacking, ignores 5% of enemy DEF. This ignore DEF increases by 5% for each time this Champion counterattacks in the same turn, up to 25%. When counterattacking, deals double damage.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion | slot inferred positionally - verify'),
  ('0ef487dc-6320-4c8b-aff6-c9159b09e9e6','C000918-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Solar Flare','Attacks all enemies. Steals 25% of each target''s Turn Meter. Deals 35% increased damage against enemies whose RES is lower than this Champion''s RES. Places a 1-turn [Block Damage] buff on this Champion.','4',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion | slot inferred positionally - verify'),
  ('0ef487dc-6320-4c8b-aff6-c9159b09e9e6','C000918-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Celestial Judgment','Attacks one enemy 3 times. Ignores [Shield], [Block Damage], and [Unkillable] buffs. Ignores 35% of enemy DEF. Places a [Block Revive] debuff on enemies whose RES is lower than this Champion''s RES. Grants an Extra Turn if the target survives.','5',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion | slot inferred positionally - verify'),
  ('0ef487dc-6320-4c8b-aff6-c9159b09e9e6','C000918-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Retribution of Light','Decreases damage received by 15% from enemies whose RES is lower than this Champion''s RES. Places a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 1 turn at the end of each turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion | slot inferred positionally - verify'),
  ('0ef487dc-6320-4c8b-aff6-c9159b09e9e6','C000918-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Lumaya''s Glory','Decreases the damage this Champion receives from enemies whose RES is lower than this Champion''s by 15%. Places on this Champion a protected [Counterattack] buff for 1 turn at the end of their turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-A1','A1','base','Sufferslash','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Has a 50% chance of removing 1 random buff from the target. [Passive Effect] Whenever an enemy hits this Champion or an ally, has a 50% chance to counterattack with this skill. This chance increases by 10% for each debuff on the enemy.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-A2','A2','base','Devilish Accord','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Before attacking, swaps HP with an enemy, then steals all buffs from them. Also transfers all debuffs from this Champion to the target, and places a [Seal] debuff on the target for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be removed. This debuff cannot be resisted or blocked if the target has 50% HP or less.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-A3','A3','base','Trinity of Pain','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. The first hit places a [Block Passive Skills] debuff for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be removed. The second hit places a [Block Active Skills] debuff for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be removed. The third hit steals 100% of the target''s Turn Meter.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-Passive','Passive','base','Avatar of Anarchy [P]','Each hit this Champion deals from skills has a 50% chance of applying a [Debuff Spread] effect, taking 1 random debuff from the target and placing it on all enemies. Whenever this Champion kills an enemy, has a 100% chance of applying a [Debuff Spread] effect, taking all debuffs from the target and placing them on all enemies. This effect cannot be resisted.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Demon Stinger','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Heals this Champion by 20% of the damage inflicted. [Passive Effect] Whenever an enemy hits this Champion or an ally, has a 50% chance to counterattack with this skill. This chance increases by 10% for each debuff on the enemy.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion | A1 contains embedded passive counterattack effect - not a separate Passive slot skill'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Singularity of Pain','Attacks all enemies. Will ignore [Shield] buffs. Will also ignore [Ally Protection] buffs when attacking enemies under 1 or more debuffs, and [Unkillable] buffs when attacking enemies under 2 or more debuffs.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Infernal Stars','Attacks all enemies 2 times. If a target is killed by this skill while under 3 or more different debuffs, places a [Block Revive] debuff on them. Also heals this Champion by 30% of the damage dealt.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('8ecd698b-784d-4c88-bd9d-67e92350013e','C000919-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Unending Karnage [P]','This Champion''s C.DMG increases by 1% for every 3 points of ACC they have. Ignores 10% of the target''s DEF for each debuff they are under.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('ab3a4318-82c2-491c-a1f2-0d3d8791edfc','C000920-A1','A1','base','Stoke Anguish','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit decreases the target''s DEF by 2% (stacks up to 20%). Each hit also steals 10% of the target''s Turn Meter.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('ab3a4318-82c2-491c-a1f2-0d3d8791edfc','C000920-A2','A2','base','Agony Overwhelming','Attacks all enemies. Removes all buffs from all enemies and places a [Block Active Skills] debuff on them for 2 turns. Also steals 20% of the Turn Meter from each enemy under a [Block Active Skills] debuff.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('ab3a4318-82c2-491c-a1f2-0d3d8791edfc','C000920-A3','A3','base','Thief of Joy','Attacks 1 enemy. Steals 100% of the target''s Turn Meter. Also, puts the target''s skills on cooldown.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
