  ('ab3a4318-82c2-491c-a1f2-0d3d8791edfc','C000920-Passive','Passive','base','Dramatis Miserae [P]','Whenever this Champion loses 30% HP or more in a single turn, deals damage to the attacker equal to 30% of this Champion''s MAX HP. Occurs once per turn. Also when this Champion loses 30% HP or more in a single turn, places a [Shield] buff on them, equal to 30% of this Champion''s MAX HP, for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('ab3a4318-82c2-491c-a1f2-0d3d8791edfc','C000920-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Volatile Performer','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 50% chance of placing a [Bomb] debuff for 2 turns. Heals this Champion by 10% of their MAX HP for each [Bomb] debuff placed.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('ab3a4318-82c2-491c-a1f2-0d3d8791edfc','C000920-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Explosive Showstopper','Attacks all enemies. Places 2 [Bomb] debuffs on all enemies for 2 turns. Instantly detonates all [Bomb] debuffs on enemies with [Stone Skin] buffs or enemies whose HP is less than this Champion''s HP. Then, places a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn on all enemies who had their [Bomb] debuffs detonated by this skill.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('ab3a4318-82c2-491c-a1f2-0d3d8791edfc','C000920-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Killer Encore','Heals this Champion by 50% of their MAX HP. Also places a 25% [Weaken] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('ab3a4318-82c2-491c-a1f2-0d3d8791edfc','C000920-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('ab3a4318-82c2-491c-a1f2-0d3d8791edfc','C000920-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','The Last Laugh [P]','Has a 100% chance to reflect all [Bomb] debuffs placed on this Champion back to an attacker. Also has a 30% chance to reflect all other debuffs placed on this Champion back to an attacker. Heals this Champion by 20% of their MAX HP whenever an enemy is killed by a [Bomb] debuff.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('cb2ee945-37d2-42d8-98de-fba6b053f626','C000921-A1','A1','base','Surge Of Chaos','Attacks all enemies. Heals all allies. The value of the heal is proportional to this Champion''s ATK.',null,null,'3','ATK',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('cb2ee945-37d2-42d8-98de-fba6b053f626','C000921-A2','A2','base','Anything For Siroth','Removes all debuffs from all allies. Then places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a [Shield] buff on all allies for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s ATK.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('cb2ee945-37d2-42d8-98de-fba6b053f626','C000921-A3','A3','base','Running Rampant','Places a [Taunt] buff and a 25% [Fortify] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Also places an [Unkillable] buff on all allies except this Champion for 2 turns.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('cb2ee945-37d2-42d8-98de-fba6b053f626','C000921-Passive','Passive','base','Collector Of Pawns','[Passive Effect] Receives 15% less damage for each alive ally. [Active Effect] Instantly transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form whenever their last living ally is killed.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('cb2ee945-37d2-42d8-98de-fba6b053f626','C000921-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Destroyer Of All','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. If this attack kills an enemy, deals pure damage to all other enemies. If the other enemies are not Bosses or Minions, the amount of pure damage dealt is equal to 30% of the initial target''s MAX HP. If the other enemies are Bosses or Minions, the pure damage is dealt equal to 10% of their MAX HP instead. This attack cannot be critical.',null,null,'1.3','ATK',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
