  ('f12dc40e-98fb-4c94-ae5a-9fa00a2d71c2','C000925-Passive','Passive','base','Blackteeth''s Buffet [P]','Whenever an enemy receives a buff, is healed, or has their Turn Meter increased by a skill, places a 5% [Poison] debuff on that enemy for 2 turns. Will ignore [Block Debuffs] buffs. Increases this Champion''s Turn Meter by 5% for each [Poison] debuff placed by this skill.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
