  ('0df56686-0cfb-43f3-979d-83a329522086','C000927-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Glacial Embrace','Places [Ensnare] and [Block Buffs] on enemies while granting [Block Debuffs] and [Strengthen] to allies.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion | slot inferred positionally - verify'),
