  ('0df56686-0cfb-43f3-979d-83a329522086','C000927-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Eternal Frost [P]','Revives allies once per round with full HP and [Freeze] on enemies for control. Removes [Freeze] from allies before their turns and places irresistible [HP Burn] on attackers.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
