  ('a1ac67e8-0c63-4515-8425-a07d9841a358','C000928-A2','A2','base','Perfection in Motion','Attacks all enemies 2 times. Each hit steals all buffs from all enemies. Then applies a [Buff Spread] effect, taking all buffs from this Champion and placing them on all allies.','4 Turns',null,'2.2','ATK',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('a1ac67e8-0c63-4515-8425-a07d9841a358','C000928-A3','A3','base','Sneer of Disdain','Attacks all enemies 2 times. Each hit increases the cooldown of 1 of each enemy''s skills to the maximum. Also decreases the Turn Meters of all enemies by 30%. Then grants an Extra Turn.','5 Turns',null,'2.2','ATK',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
