  ('a1ac67e8-0c63-4515-8425-a07d9841a358','C000928-Passive','Passive','base','Is That... It?','This Champion receives no damage when attacked by enemies, including Bosses and their minions, out of their active turn. All allies except this Champion deal 3% more damage for each enemy skill that has had its cooldown increased by this Champion (stacks up to 25%). If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This skill will not activate on duplicate copies of this Champion, if this particular Champion is dead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('a1ac67e8-0c63-4515-8425-a07d9841a358','C000928-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Wrath of Superiority','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. Will ignore [Block Damage] and [Unkillable] buffs. Instantly activates this skill against an enemy whenever that enemy receives a [Block Damage] or [Unkillable] buff, or has their death prevented by themselves or allies. Occurs once per turn.',null,null,'1.5','ATK',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('a1ac67e8-0c63-4515-8425-a07d9841a358','C000928-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Pinions of Wrath','Attacks all enemies 2 times. Before attacking, swaps HP with a target enemy. For this skill, increases this Champion''s ATK and decreases all enemies'' DEF by a percentage equal to the percentage of HP swapped.',null,null,'2.5','ATK',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('a1ac67e8-0c63-4515-8425-a07d9841a358','C000928-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','You Will Weep','Attacks all enemies 2 times. Will ignore 25% of the target''s DEF. Before attacking, decreases the value of any [Stone Skin], [Shield], and [Magma Shield] buffs by 75%. This effect cannot be resisted if target has any skills on cooldown. Places a protected [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s ATK.',null,null,'2.1','ATK',0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('a1ac67e8-0c63-4515-8425-a07d9841a358','C000928-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Behold My Majesty','This Champion''s attacks are always critical against enemies that have any skills on cooldown. This Champion''s skills deal 3% more damage for each turn of cooldown remaining on all enemy skills.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('2341c4f3-f43c-4671-8c30-bed99ca6c9a7','C000929-A1','A1','base','Excoriating Edge','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. The first hit transfers all debuffs from this Champion to the target. The second hit then increases the duration of all debuffs on the target by 1 turn.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('2341c4f3-f43c-4671-8c30-bed99ca6c9a7','C000929-A2','A2','base','Seraphic Wave','Attacks all enemies. Each critical hit fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 25%. Resets the cooldown of the Rage of the Nephilim skill if this attack kills an enemy. Resets the cooldown of all of this Champion''s skills if this attack kills 2 or more enemies.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion'),
  ('2341c4f3-f43c-4671-8c30-bed99ca6c9a7','C000929-A3','A3','base','Rage of the Nephilim','Attacks 1 enemy. Ignores 50% of the target''s DEF. Will attack all remaining enemies with any surplus damage if the initial target is killed. Fully heals this Champion if the initial hit kills an enemy.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-09; Mythical champion')
