  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-A1','A1','base','Allpiercer','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore [Shield], [Unkillable], and [Block Damage] buffs.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-A2','A2','base','Blackfeather Barrage','Attacks all enemies. This attack will not trigger counterattacks and ignores [Shield] buffs. Also steals 20% of the Turn Meter from each enemy. This effect cannot be resisted by enemies with more than 50% Turn Meter.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-A3','A3','base','Thief''s Omen','Attacks 1 enemy. Deals double damage to bosses. Destroys the target''s MAX HP and decreases the target''s ATK, DEF, SPD, RES and ACC by 10% when this Champion hits them with this skill for the first time. This effect does not work against Bosses. Also increases this Champion''s MAX HP, ATK, DEF, SPD, RES and ACC by 10% each time this Champion decreases enemy stats with this skill. Finally, places a [Block Revive] debuff if the target is killed by this skill.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-Passive','Passive','base','Glinting Saviour [P]','Deals 5% more damage for each 10% HP the target has lost. Also prevents this Champion''s death and keeps them alive on 1 HP when hit with a fatal hit, then transforms them into their Alternate Form.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion | passive skill with active effect - CD 4 applies to active component only'),
  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Fae Talons','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit heals this Champion by 7.5% of their MAX HP. If this Champion''s HP is full, each hit fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 15% instead.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Murder of Crows','Attacks all enemies. Places a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn if this Champion has more than 50% HP. This debuff cannot be resisted if this Champion has more than 75% HP. If this Champion has 50% HP or less, places a [Stun] debuff for 1 turn instead. This debuff cannot be resisted.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Feathershield','Removes all debuffs from this Champion. Places a number of 15% [Continuous Heal] buffs on this Champion, equal to the amount of debuffs removed by this skill. Also places a [Counterattack] buff and a [Block Damage] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. These buffs cannot be removed, stolen or transferred.','6 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-ALT-A4','A4','alternate','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Base Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('a3efe80a-1372-4614-8f55-25849028d5eb','C000924-ALT-Passive','Passive','alternate','Fae Intervention [P]','Increases this Champion''s MAX HP, DEF, SPD, RES, and ACC by 15% for every dead enemy and ally, including Bosses and their minions, in battle (stacks up to 100%). Also revives 1 random ally with 50% HP and 50% Turn Meter each time this Champion kills an enemy.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('917262ec-3487-440e-b2d9-9984d3e2b9a9','C000912-A1','A1','base','Bite of the Wolf','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 50% chance of placing a [Freeze] debuff for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be blocked or resisted if the target Champion is from the Gaellen Pact. If the target is not under a [Freeze] debuff, will repeat the attack once.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('917262ec-3487-440e-b2d9-9984d3e2b9a9','C000912-A2','A2','base','Great Captain','Places a [Block Debuffs] buff and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Decreases the cooldown of all ally skills, except this Champion''s, by 1 turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('917262ec-3487-440e-b2d9-9984d3e2b9a9','C000912-A3','A3','base','Wolfheart''s Rage','Attacks all enemies. Places a [Freeze] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn, and a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. If an enemy is from the Gaellen Pact, places a [Freeze] debuff on them for 2 turns instead and this debuff cannot be blocked or resisted. Also decreases the target''s Turn Meter by 30%. If the enemy is from the Gaellen Pact, decreases their Turn Meter by 50% instead. Grants an Extra Turn.','5 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('917262ec-3487-440e-b2d9-9984d3e2b9a9','C000912-A4','A4','base','Metamorph','Transforms this Champion into their Alternate Form. Then grants an Extra Turn.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('917262ec-3487-440e-b2d9-9984d3e2b9a9','C000912-Passive','Passive','base','Best Served Cold [P]','Whenever this Champion or an ally receives a debuff from an enemy, has a 30% chance of placing a [Freeze] debuff on that enemy for 1 turn. This chance increases to 100% and the debuff cannot be blocked or resisted if the target is from the Gaellen Pact.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('917262ec-3487-440e-b2d9-9984d3e2b9a9','C000912-ALT-A1','A1','alternate','Rimecleave','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore 15% of the target''s DEF. If the target is under a [Freeze] debuff, ignores 35% of the target''s DEF instead. If this attack kills an enemy, resets the cooldown of one of this Champion''s random skills.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('917262ec-3487-440e-b2d9-9984d3e2b9a9','C000912-ALT-A2','A2','alternate','Icequake','Attacks all enemies. Places an extra hit on enemies under [Freeze], [Stun], [Fear], [True Fear], [Provoke], or [Petrification] debuffs. Each hit decreases each target''s MAX HP by 25% of the damage inflicted (stacks up to 50%). Each hit also decreases each target''s Turn Meter by 25%. This effect cannot be resisted if an enemy is under [Freeze], [Stun], [Fear], [True Fear], [Provoke], or [Petrification] debuffs.','3 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
  ('917262ec-3487-440e-b2d9-9984d3e2b9a9','C000912-ALT-A3','A3','alternate','Disciple of Tormin','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore 50% of the target''s DEF. If the target is under a [Freeze] debuff, will ignore 100% of the target''s DEF and [Block Damage] buffs instead. If the target is killed while under a [Freeze] debuff, also places a [Block Revive] debuff on them, and places a [Freeze] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. The [Freeze] debuff cannot be blocked or resisted by enemies from the Gaellen Pact.','4 Turns',null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','human_observation; web-sourced 2026-07-10; Mythical champion'),
