  ('9d2b6aae-71de-4a34-a92a-3b8786c783a0','C000621-P','Passive','base','Spirit of the North','If an ally is under 2 or more buffs, increases their RES by 50. If an ally is under 3 or more buffs, also increases their ACC by 50. If an ally is under 4 or more buffs, also increases their damage dealt by 20%.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: If an ally is under 2 or more buffs, increases their RES by 50. If an ally is under 3 or more buffs, also increases their ACC by 50. If an ally is under 4 or more buffs, also increases their damage dealt by 20%.'),
  ('d83595d1-8abe-44f5-a1bb-9c0c45719ca0','C000788-A1','A1','base','Spirit Thrust','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 50% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns. If the target is a Boss, this debuff cannot be resisted.','0','0','3.2','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 50% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns. If the target is a Boss, this debuff cannot be resisted. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff chance +5% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 3.2 ATK'),
  ('d83595d1-8abe-44f5-a1bb-9c0c45719ca0','C000788-A2','A2','base','Spirit Step Slash','Attacks 1 enemy. Every second use of this skill in a Round will attack all enemies instead. Will also ignore 25% of the target''s DEF. If the target is a boss, will ignore 100% of the target''s DEF.','4','3','4','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Every second use of this skill in a Round will attack all enemies instead. Will also ignore 25% of the target''s DEF. If the target is a boss, will ignore 100% of the target''s DEF. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Damage +5% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 4 ATK'),
  ('d83595d1-8abe-44f5-a1bb-9c0c45719ca0','C000788-A3','A3','base','Overhead Slash','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 30% [Increase C.DMG] buff and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on this Champion for 2 turns.','4','3','4.1','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 30% [Increase C.DMG] buff and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Damage +5% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 4.1 ATK'),
  ('d83595d1-8abe-44f5-a1bb-9c0c45719ca0','C000788-P','Passive','base','Rathalos Mastery','Inflicts 50% more damage against targets under [HP Burn] debuffs. Receives 25% less damage from enemies under [HP Burn] debuffs. Every fifth skill used by this Champion deals 200% more damage.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Inflicts 50% more damage against targets under [HP Burn] debuffs. Receives 25% less damage from enemies under [HP Burn] debuffs. Every fifth skill used by this Champion deals 200% more damage.'),
  ('cd705c45-37b2-4943-9e77-a1d6775a2dc7','C000851-A1','A1','base','Demonbreaker','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, has a 25% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. Has a 50% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns, if the target is from the Corrupted Alliance, a Boss or a minion. This effect cannot be resisted by enemies from the Corrupted Alliance, Bosses or minions. Grants an Extra Turn if a [Weaken] debuff was placed on all enemies by this skill.','0','0','2.5','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, has a 25% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. Has a 50% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns, if the target is from the Corrupted Alliance, a Boss or a minion. This effect cannot be resisted by enemies from the Corrupted Alliance, Bosses or minions. Grants an Extra Turn if a [Weaken] debuff was placed on all enemies by this skill. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff chance +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff chance +15% Damage Multiplier: 2.5 ATK'),
  ('cd705c45-37b2-4943-9e77-a1d6775a2dc7','C000851-A2','A2','base','Back to the Abyss','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit will ignore 25% of the target''s DEF. If the target is from the Corrupted Alliance, a Boss or a minion, each hit ignores 50% of the target''s DEF instead. Each hit decreases the target''s ATK by 5% (stacks up to 25%). Each hit also increases this Champion''s ATK by 5% (stacks up to 50%).','4','3','2.4','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit will ignore 25% of the target''s DEF. If the target is from the Corrupted Alliance, a Boss or a minion, each hit ignores 50% of the target''s DEF instead. Each hit decreases the target''s ATK by 5% (stacks up to 25%). Each hit also increases this Champion''s ATK by 5% (stacks up to 50%). Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 2.4 ATK'),
  ('cd705c45-37b2-4943-9e77-a1d6775a2dc7','C000851-A3','A3','base','Rabid Fury','Attacks all enemies 2 times. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. For each critical hit landed on the first hit, increases the damage dealt on the second hit by 10%. Will ignore [Unkillable] and [Shield] buffs.','4','3','2','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies 2 times. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. For each critical hit landed on the first hit, increases the damage dealt on the second hit by 10%. Will ignore [Unkillable] and [Shield] buffs. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 2 ATK'),
  ('cd705c45-37b2-4943-9e77-a1d6775a2dc7','C000851-P','Passive','base','Evil''s Nightmare','Activates Demonbreaker skill every fifth turn this Champion takes. Enemies from the Corrupted Alliance, a Bosses and minion cannot land critical hits on this Champion.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Activates Demonbreaker skill every fifth turn this Champion takes. Enemies from the Corrupted Alliance, a Bosses and minion cannot land critical hits on this Champion.'),
  ('1cd23b1a-2dba-4cdb-9094-8df06c3f5828','C000853-A1','A1','base','Carnival Hammer','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit heals this Champion by 10% of their MAX HP. If the target has no active buffs, each hit also fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 10%.','0','0','0.1','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit heals this Champion by 10% of their MAX HP. If the target has no active buffs, each hit also fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 10%. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Heal +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Heal +10% Damage Multiplier: 0.1 HP'),
  ('1cd23b1a-2dba-4cdb-9094-8df06c3f5828','C000853-A2','A2','base','Test Your Strength','Attacks all enemies. Decreases the duration of all enemy buffs by 3 turns. If there are no enemies with active buffs, grants an Extra Turn. Always grants an Extra Turn if Kaja the Wry is on the same team, even if there are enemies with active buffs.','6','4','0.25','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Decreases the duration of all enemy buffs by 3 turns. If there are no enemies with active buffs, grants an Extra Turn. Always grants an Extra Turn if Kaja the Wry is on the same team, even if there are enemies with active buffs. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 0.25 HP'),
  ('1cd23b1a-2dba-4cdb-9094-8df06c3f5828','C000853-A3','A3','base','Kegs of Dread','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Places a [True Fear] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn.','6','4','0.27','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Places a [True Fear] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 0.27 HP'),
  ('1cd23b1a-2dba-4cdb-9094-8df06c3f5828','C000853-P','Passive','base','Hideous Assistant','Whenever an enemy skill successfully activates while they are under a [Fear] or a [True Fear] debuff, fills Timit''s Turn Meter by 10%. Whenever an enemy skill does not activate because they are under a [Fear] or a [True Fear] debuff, places a [Provoke] debuff on that enemy for 1 turn. This particular effect only applies when Kaja the Wry is on the same team.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Whenever an enemy skill successfully activates while they are under a [Fear] or a [True Fear] debuff, fills Timit''s Turn Meter by 10%. Whenever an enemy skill does not activate because they are under a [Fear] or a [True Fear] debuff, places a [Provoke] debuff on that enemy for 1 turn. This particular effect only applies when Kaja the Wry is on the same team.'),
  ('45c27264-e41b-4593-bd03-c60f147bef2a','C000854-A1','A1','base','Ravenblade','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 40% chance of placing a [Block Active Skills] debuff for 2 turns. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Shield] buff. Whenever an ally counterattacks, teams up with allies to attack, or instantly activates a skill, also has a 40% chance to place a [Block Active Skills] debuff for 2 turns on the target enemy. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.','0','0','3.5','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 40% chance of placing a [Block Active Skills] debuff for 2 turns. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Shield] buff. Whenever an ally counterattacks, teams up with allies to attack, or instantly activates a skill, also has a 40% chance to place a [Block Active Skills] debuff for 2 turns on the target enemy. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 3.5 DEF'),
  ('45c27264-e41b-4593-bd03-c60f147bef2a','C000854-A2','A2','base','Student of War','Attacks 1 enemy. This attack is always critical if this Champion is under a [Shield] buff. This attack also gains a damage boost equal to the value of the [Shield]. Removes all debuffs from all allies if the target is killed. If the target survives, places a [Provoke] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn instead. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Shield] buff.','5','3','5.5 DEF * (1 + SHIELDS_TOTAL_VALUE/HP)','formula',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. This attack is always critical if this Champion is under a [Shield] buff. This attack also gains a damage boost equal to the value of the [Shield]. Removes all debuffs from all allies if the target is killed. If the target survives, places a [Provoke] debuff on all enemies for 1 turn instead. This effect cannot be resisted if this Champion is under a [Shield] buff. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 5.5 DEF * (1 + SHIELDS_TOTAL_VALUE/HP)'),
  ('45c27264-e41b-4593-bd03-c60f147bef2a','C000854-A3','A3','base','Androc''s Confidant','Places a 50% [Ally Protection] buff, a 50% [Increase ATK] buff, and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on a single ally for 2 turns. Also fills that ally''s Turn Meter by 40%. Instantly activates this skill at the end of an ally''s turn if that ally has no buffs and their HP is lower than 100%. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.','5','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Places a 50% [Ally Protection] buff, a 50% [Increase ATK] buff, and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on a single ally for 2 turns. Also fills that ally''s Turn Meter by 40%. Instantly activates this skill at the end of an ally''s turn if that ally has no buffs and their HP is lower than 100%. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('45c27264-e41b-4593-bd03-c60f147bef2a','C000854-P','Passive','base','For Lord & Land','Each time an enemy hits an ally, that ally''s next attack will deal 10% more damage for each hit they take (stacks up to 100%). The damage increase resets after that ally deals damage.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Each time an enemy hits an ally, that ally''s next attack will deal 10% more damage for each hit they take (stacks up to 100%). The damage increase resets after that ally deals damage.'),
  ('8793e62a-af0c-436c-b718-3209006beb9a','C000855-A1','A1','base','Mash and Mangle','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 70% chance of applying a [Buff Spread] effect, taking 1 random buff from each ally and placing it on all allies.','0','0','5.7','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 70% chance of applying a [Buff Spread] effect, taking 1 random buff from each ally and placing it on all allies. Level 2: Buff/Debuff Chance +5% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +5% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 5.7 ATK'),
  ('8793e62a-af0c-436c-b718-3209006beb9a','C000855-A2','A2','base','Grub''s Up!','Heals all allies by 20% of this Champion''s MAX HP. Places a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a 15% [Continuous Heal] buff and a [Block Debuffs] buff on all allies for 2 turns.','5','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Heals all allies by 20% of this Champion''s MAX HP. Places a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a 15% [Continuous Heal] buff and a [Block Debuffs] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('8793e62a-af0c-436c-b718-3209006beb9a','C000855-A3','A3','base','Brothers'' Generosity','Removes all debuffs from all allies. Increases the Turn Meters of all allies by 20% plus an additional 2% for each debuff removed. Then places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns.','5','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Removes all debuffs from all allies. Increases the Turn Meters of all allies by 20% plus an additional 2% for each debuff removed. Then places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('8793e62a-af0c-436c-b718-3209006beb9a','C000855-P','Passive','base','Fill Your Bellies','Increases allies'' damage dealt by 10% if they currently have less HP than their target. If an ally''s HP is equal to or greater than their target''s, increases their damage dealt by 20% instead. Increases this Champion''s and each ally''s MAX HP by 10% every time this Champion uses an active skill (stacks up to 50%). Resets each Round. Also increases each ally''s MAX HP by 5% every time they use an active skill (stacks up to 50%). Resets each Round. Will not increase the MAX HP of Bosses.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Increases allies'' damage dealt by 10% if they currently have less HP than their target. If an ally''s HP is equal to or greater than their target''s, increases their damage dealt by 20% instead. Increases this Champion''s and each ally''s MAX HP by 10% every time this Champion uses an active skill (stacks up to 50%). Resets each Round. Also increases each ally''s MAX HP by 5% every time they use an active skill (stacks up to 50%). Resets each Round. Will not increase the MAX HP of Bosses.'),
  ('6d374e05-a1c6-4225-af82-a33fba40c15a','C000859-A1','A1','base','Snakebiter','Attacks 1 enemy. Places a [True Fear] debuff on the target for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be resisted or blocked if this Champion is dead. If this Champion is dead, also heals all allies by 20% of their MAX HP.','0','0','3.5','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Places a [True Fear] debuff on the target for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be resisted or blocked if this Champion is dead. If this Champion is dead, also heals all allies by 20% of their MAX HP. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Damage Multiplier: 3.5 DEF'),
  ('6d374e05-a1c6-4225-af82-a33fba40c15a','C000859-A2','A2','base','Battle Resurrection','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore 100% of the target''s DEF. If the target was killed, revives a random dead ally with 50% HP and 50% Turn Meter. If the target was killed and there are no dead allies, resets the cooldown of this skill instead.','4','4','5','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore 100% of the target''s DEF. If the target was killed, revives a random dead ally with 50% HP and 50% Turn Meter. If the target was killed and there are no dead allies, resets the cooldown of this skill instead. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Damage Multiplier: 5 DEF'),
  ('6d374e05-a1c6-4225-af82-a33fba40c15a','C000859-A3','A3','base','For Valdemar!','Attack all enemies. Destroys the MAX HP of all enemies by 10%. Places a [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is equal to the total amount of all enemies'' destroyed MAX HP. [Undead Hordes Unity: 1 Faction Ally: The Shield buff placed by this skill cannot be removed. 2 Faction Ally: Instantly activates this skill whenever this Champion is revived. 3 Faction Ally: Will ignore a portion of each target''s DEF equal to the percentage of each target''s destroyed MAX HP.]','4','3','3.9','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attack all enemies. Destroys the MAX HP of all enemies by 10%. Places a [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is equal to the total amount of all enemies'' destroyed MAX HP. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 3.9 DEF Shield Multiplier: 1.5% Enemy Destroyed HP (Boss) OR 100% Enemy Destroyed HP (Non-Boss) [Undead Hordes Unity: 1 Faction Ally: The Shield buff placed by this skill cannot be removed. 2 Faction Ally: Instantly activates this skill whenever this Champion is revived. 3 Faction Ally: Will ignore a portion of each target''s DEF equal to the percentage of each target''s destroyed MAX HP.]'),
  ('6d374e05-a1c6-4225-af82-a33fba40c15a','C000859-P','Passive','base','Immortal Oath','Whenever this Champion is revived, increases the damage inflicted by this Champion by 20%. [Undead Hordes Unity: 1 Faction Ally: Immune to Block Revive debuffs. 2 Faction Ally: Allies receive 20% less damage if this Champion is dead. 3 Faction Ally: Whenever this Champion is dead and an ally attacks an enemy, this Champion joins that attack using their default skill.]','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Whenever this Champion is revived, increases the damage inflicted by this Champion by 20%. [Undead Hordes Unity: 1 Faction Ally: Immune to Block Revive debuffs. 2 Faction Ally: Allies receive 20% less damage if this Champion is dead. 3 Faction Ally: Whenever this Champion is dead and an ally attacks an enemy, this Champion joins that attack using their default skill.]'),
  ('3a73a65e-0c18-49b6-add0-38d151ba84db','C000865-A1','A1','base','Wyrmwrath','Attacks 1 enemy. Has an 80% chance of stealing a random buff from the enemy. Also has an 80% chance of placing a [Block Buffs] debuff on the enemy for 2 turns.','0','0','0.23','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Has an 80% chance of stealing a random buff from the enemy. Also has an 80% chance of placing a [Block Buffs] debuff on the enemy for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Damage +5% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 0.23 HP'),
  ('3a73a65e-0c18-49b6-add0-38d151ba84db','C000865-A2','A2','base','Earth Puncture','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of removing all buffs from all enemies. Then, has a 75% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns.','4','3','0.25','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of removing all buffs from all enemies. Then, has a 75% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 0.25 HP'),
  ('3a73a65e-0c18-49b6-add0-38d151ba84db','C000865-A3','A3','base','Ogryn Fortitude','Places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff on all allies whose DEF is higher than or equal to their ATK for 2 turns. If an ally''s ATK is higher than their DEF, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on them for 2 turns instead.','5','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff on all allies whose DEF is higher than or equal to their ATK for 2 turns. If an ally''s ATK is higher than their DEF, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on them for 2 turns instead. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('3a73a65e-0c18-49b6-add0-38d151ba84db','C000865-P','Passive','base','Scourge of Dragons','Whenever an enemy is revived, instantly activates [Earth Puncture]. If an enemy is revived by a Champion from the Lizardmen Faction, the effects of [Earth Puncture] cannot be resisted. This passive effect will only activate when an enemy is revived using an active skill. Instantly activating [Earth Puncture] will not place the skill on cooldown. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.','2','1',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Whenever an enemy is revived, instantly activates [Earth Puncture]. If an enemy is revived by a Champion from the Lizardmen Faction, the effects of [Earth Puncture] cannot be resisted. This passive effect will only activate when an enemy is revived using an active skill. Instantly activating [Earth Puncture] will not place the skill on cooldown. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. Level 2: Cooldown -1'),
  ('7ea96637-2885-4f96-bace-a11b701fd9ca','C000866-A1','A1','base','Under The Skin','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 50% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns. Each hit will also ignore 50% of the target''s RES if Oella is on the same team. If the target is under an [Increase DEF] buff, each hit has a 80% chance of removing it. This effect cannot be resisted.','0','0','1.6','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 50% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff for 2 turns. Each hit will also ignore 50% of the target''s RES if Oella is on the same team. If the target is under an [Increase DEF] buff, each hit has a 80% chance of removing it. This effect cannot be resisted. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 1.6 ATK'),
  ('7ea96637-2885-4f96-bace-a11b701fd9ca','C000866-A2','A2','base','Resurging Reversal','Removes all debuffs from this Champion and heals them by 20% of their MAX HP. Heals this Champion by an additional 20% of their MAX HP for each debuff removed. Then, places a [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s ATK. The value of the [Shield] also increases by 5% for each debuff removed. Finally, attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore [Shield] buffs. Damage increases by 20% for each debuff removed by this skill.','4','3','5','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Removes all debuffs from this Champion and heals them by 20% of their MAX HP. Heals this Champion by an additional 20% of their MAX HP for each debuff removed. Then, places a [Shield] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s ATK. The value of the [Shield] also increases by 5% for each debuff removed. Finally, attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore [Shield] buffs. Damage increases by 20% for each debuff removed by this skill. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 5 ATK Shield Multiplier: 4 ATK'),
  ('7ea96637-2885-4f96-bace-a11b701fd9ca','C000866-A3','A3','base','Somnolence Spores','Attacks all enemies. Has a 100% chance of placing a [Sleep] debuff for 1 turn and a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns. If Oella is on the same team, will place a [Stun] debuff instead of [Sleep], and ignore 50% of each target''s RES. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 15% whenever a [Sleep] or [Stun] debuff placed by this skill expires. If Oella is on the same team, grants this Champion an Extra Turn.','5','4','4.1','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Has a 100% chance of placing a [Sleep] debuff for 1 turn and a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns. If Oella is on the same team, will place a [Stun] debuff instead of [Sleep], and ignore 50% of each target''s RES. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 15% whenever a [Sleep] or [Stun] debuff placed by this skill expires. If Oella is on the same team, grants this Champion an Extra Turn. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 4.1 ATK'),
  ('7ea96637-2885-4f96-bace-a11b701fd9ca','C000866-P','Passive','base','Metabolism','Has a 15% chance of decreasing the cooldown of one of this Champion''s skills by 1 turn every time they are healed by a [Continuous Heal] buff. The chance increases to 30% if Oella is on the same team.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Has a 15% chance of decreasing the cooldown of one of this Champion''s skills by 1 turn every time they are healed by a [Continuous Heal] buff. The chance increases to 30% if Oella is on the same team.'),
  ('48249fbe-4ff2-4ff5-8770-b0587316fd88','C000871-A1','A1','base','Ruthless Axmaster','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 20% chance of granting an Extra Turn. If this attack kills an enemy, grants an Extra Turn.','0','0','3.7','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 20% chance of granting an Extra Turn. If this attack kills an enemy, grants an Extra Turn. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Damage +5% Level 4: Damage +5% Level 5: Damage +5% Damage Multiplier: 3.7 ATK'),
  ('48249fbe-4ff2-4ff5-8770-b0587316fd88','C000871-A2','A2','base','Stone-Hearted','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, reduces the value of any [Shield] buffs on all enemies by 100%, and places a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff on them for 2 turns. These effects cannot be resisted if this skill was used on an Extra Turn. Has a 20% chance of granting an Extra Turn. This chance increases by 10% for each critical hit.','4','3','4','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, reduces the value of any [Shield] buffs on all enemies by 100%, and places a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff on them for 2 turns. These effects cannot be resisted if this skill was used on an Extra Turn. Has a 20% chance of granting an Extra Turn. This chance increases by 10% for each critical hit. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Damage +5% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 4 ATK'),
  ('48249fbe-4ff2-4ff5-8770-b0587316fd88','C000871-A3','A3','base','Royal Fury','Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore [Shield], [Block Damage], and [Unkillable] buffs. Also ignores [Stone Skin] buffs and 100% of the target''s DEF if this skill was used on an Extra Turn or an Instant Turn.','4','3','5.5','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Will ignore [Shield], [Block Damage], and [Unkillable] buffs. Also ignores [Stone Skin] buffs and 100% of the target''s DEF if this skill was used on an Extra Turn or an Instant Turn. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 5.5 ATK'),
  ('48249fbe-4ff2-4ff5-8770-b0587316fd88','C000871-P','Passive','base','Jade King','Increases the chance for all allies to gain an Extra Turn by 5%. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This Champion deals 25% more damage on Extra Turns.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Increases the chance for all allies to gain an Extra Turn by 5%. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. This Champion deals 25% more damage on Extra Turns.'),
  ('45de3969-2b93-4f1d-9f91-e66ef1fde65a','C000872-A1','A1','base','Dread Scythe','Attacks 1 enemy. This attack ignores [Shield] buffs. Has a 60% chance of increasing the duration of all debuffs on the target by one turn. Also has an 80% chance of applying a [Debuff Spread] effect, taking 2 random debuffs from the target and placing them on all enemies under a [Hex] debuff.','0','0','3.6','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. This attack ignores [Shield] buffs. Has a 60% chance of increasing the duration of all debuffs on the target by one turn. Also has an 80% chance of applying a [Debuff Spread] effect, taking 2 random debuffs from the target and placing them on all enemies under a [Hex] debuff. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 6: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 3.6 ATK'),
  ('45de3969-2b93-4f1d-9f91-e66ef1fde65a','C000872-A2','A2','base','Hex of Blades','Attacks all enemies. This attack deals single-target damage to each target individually, rather than AOE damage. Before attacking, has an 80% chance of placing a [Hex] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Will ignore 20% of each enemy''s RES for each dead ally. Damage of this skill increases by 10% for each debuff on each enemy.','4','3','4.2 ATK + (4.2 ATK * 0.1 * Debuff Count)','formula',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. This attack deals single-target damage to each target individually, rather than AOE damage. Before attacking, has an 80% chance of placing a [Hex] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Will ignore 20% of each enemy''s RES for each dead ally. Damage of this skill increases by 10% for each debuff on each enemy. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 6: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 4.2 ATK + (4.2 ATK * 0.1 * Debuff Count)'),
  ('45de3969-2b93-4f1d-9f91-e66ef1fde65a','C000872-A3','A3','base','Death''s Bargain','Target an ally. If the ally is alive, kills them and unlocks a Secret Skill, [Malice Unleashed]. Also places a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns and [True Fear] debuff for 1 turn on all enemies. These debuffs cannot be resisted or blocked, fills this champion''s Turn meter by 75%. If the ally is dead, heals this champion by 50% of the dead ally''s MAX HP. If all allies are dead, also unlocks a secret skill, [Malice Unleashed]. Places a [Shield] buff on this champion for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is equal to any surplus heal. If this champion already has a [Shield] buff, the value of the [Shield] is increased by any surplus heal. Then, fills this champion''s Turn Meter by 75%.','5','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Target an ally. If the ally is alive, kills them and unlocks a Secret Skill, [Malice Unleashed]. Also places a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns and [True Fear] debuff for 1 turn on all enemies. These debuffs cannot be resisted or blocked, fills this champion''s Turn meter by 75%. If the ally is dead, heals this champion by 50% of the dead ally''s MAX HP. If all allies are dead, also unlocks a secret skill, [Malice Unleashed]. Places a [Shield] buff on this champion for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is equal to any surplus heal. If this champion already has a [Shield] buff, the value of the [Shield] is increased by any surplus heal. Then, fills this champion''s Turn Meter by 75%. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('45de3969-2b93-4f1d-9f91-e66ef1fde65a','C000872-SECRET','Secret','base','Malice Unleashed','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, steals all buffs from the target. This effect cannot be resisted. If the target has ATK equal or higher than this champion''s ATK, this attack gains a bonus damage multiplier, equal to the target''s ATK. Not applicable to Bosses. If the target''s ATK is less than this Champion''s ATK, this attack will ignore 50% of the target''s DEF. This attack will also ignore [Block Damage], [Unkillable], [Shield] and [Ally Protection] buffs. Places a [Block Revive] debuff if the target is killed.','0','0','7.5 ATK Damage Multiplier vs Champions: 7.5 ATK + Target Attack if Target has more Attack','formula',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, steals all buffs from the target. This effect cannot be resisted. If the target has ATK equal or higher than this champion''s ATK, this attack gains a bonus damage multiplier, equal to the target''s ATK. Not applicable to Bosses. If the target''s ATK is less than this Champion''s ATK, this attack will ignore 50% of the target''s DEF. This attack will also ignore [Block Damage], [Unkillable], [Shield] and [Ally Protection] buffs. Places a [Block Revive] debuff if the target is killed. Damage Multiplier vs Boss: 7.5 ATK Damage Multiplier vs Champions: 7.5 ATK + Target Attack if Target has more Attack'),
  ('45de3969-2b93-4f1d-9f91-e66ef1fde65a','C000872-P','Passive','base','Phantom Bulwark','[Active Effect] Places a [Shield] buff on this champion each time an ally or enemy champion dies. The value of the [Shield] buff is equal to 50% of the dead champion MAX HP. This [Shield] buff cannot be removed, stolen or transferred. If this Champion is already under a [Shield] buff, the value of the [Shield] is increased by 50% of the dead champion''s MAX HP. Does not activate when a boss or minion dies. [Passive Effect] Whenever an enemy hits this champion while they are under a [Shield] buff, places a random debuff on the attacking enemy. [Fear], [True Fear], [Freeze], [Provoke], [Petrification], [Sleep] and [Stun] debuffs are placed for 1 turn. Any other debuffs are placed for 2 turns. Will ignore 20% of enemy RES for each dead ally. Cannot place Boss-exclusive debuffs, [Sheep] or [Smite] debuffs.','1','1',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: [Active Effect] Places a [Shield] buff on this champion each time an ally or enemy champion dies. The value of the [Shield] buff is equal to 50% of the dead champion MAX HP. This [Shield] buff cannot be removed, stolen or transferred. If this Champion is already under a [Shield] buff, the value of the [Shield] is increased by 50% of the dead champion''s MAX HP. Does not activate when a boss or minion dies. [Passive Effect] Whenever an enemy hits this champion while they are under a [Shield] buff, places a random debuff on the attacking enemy. [Fear], [True Fear], [Freeze], [Provoke], [Petrification], [Sleep] and [Stun] debuffs are placed for 1 turn. Any other debuffs are placed for 2 turns. Will ignore 20% of enemy RES for each dead ally. Cannot place Boss-exclusive debuffs, [Sheep] or [Smite] debuffs.'),
  ('94826114-c84b-4adc-b1d4-23ab05eb6672','C000874-A1','A1','base','Hulking Killer','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Will ignore [Unkillable] buffs. When counterattacking, will attack 3 times instead.','0','0','2','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Will ignore [Unkillable] buffs. When counterattacking, will attack 3 times instead. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Damage Multiplier: 2 DEF'),
  ('94826114-c84b-4adc-b1d4-23ab05eb6672','C000874-A2','A2','base','Murderous Fighter','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Will ignore [Block Damage] and [Shield] buffs. Whenever this Champion teams up with an ally to attack an enemy, they will use this skill. When joining an ally''s attack, will attack 3 times instead.','4','3','2.8','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Will ignore [Block Damage] and [Shield] buffs. Whenever this Champion teams up with an ally to attack an enemy, they will use this skill. When joining an ally''s attack, will attack 3 times instead. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 2.8 DEF'),
  ('94826114-c84b-4adc-b1d4-23ab05eb6672','C000874-A3','A3','base','Brutish Dominance','Places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff, a [Counterattack] buff, and a 15% [Shatter] buff on this Champion for 3 turns. Then grants an Extra Turn.','6','4',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff, a [Counterattack] buff, and a 15% [Shatter] buff on this Champion for 3 turns. Then grants an Extra Turn. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('94826114-c84b-4adc-b1d4-23ab05eb6672','C000874-P','Passive','base','Instrument of Power','Has a 15% chance to join an attack whenever an ally attacks an enemy. The chance increases to 25% when an ally from the Dark Elves Faction attacks. Enemies killed by this Champion whenever they counterattack or join in an ally''s attack cannot be revived.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Has a 15% chance to join an attack whenever an ally attacks an enemy. The chance increases to 25% when an ally from the Dark Elves Faction attacks. Enemies killed by this Champion whenever they counterattack or join in an ally''s attack cannot be revived.'),
  ('bcf948cb-ef87-4a46-b5ed-ac5e296548e4','C000877-A1','A1','base','Deadbolt','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 40% chance of placing a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn. If the target is a Boss, the chance increases to 80%.','0','0','1.5','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit has a 40% chance of placing a [Provoke] debuff for 1 turn. If the target is a Boss, the chance increases to 80%. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 1.5 DEF'),
  ('bcf948cb-ef87-4a46-b5ed-ac5e296548e4','C000877-A2','A2','base','Tempest of Knowledge','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns. Also increases the duration of all ally buffs by 1 turn. Then increases the value of all [Shield]s on all allies. The value of each [Shield] is increased proportional to the total number of buffs which had their duration increased.','4','3','3.5','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns. Also increases the duration of all ally buffs by 1 turn. Then increases the value of all [Shield]s on all allies. The value of each [Shield] is increased proportional to the total number of buffs which had their duration increased. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Level 6: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 3.5 DEF'),
  ('bcf948cb-ef87-4a46-b5ed-ac5e296548e4','C000877-A3','A3','base','Codex Intercipio','Places 2 [Intercept] stacks on a target ally. Also places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff and a [Shield] buff on all allies for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s DEF.','5','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Places 2 [Intercept] stacks on a target ally. Also places a 60% [Increase DEF] buff and a [Shield] buff on all allies for 2 turns. The value of the [Shield] is proportional to this Champion''s DEF. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('bcf948cb-ef87-4a46-b5ed-ac5e296548e4','C000877-P','Passive','base','Isolated Lunacy','At the start of each round, places a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 1 turn. This buff cannot be removed. At the end of this Champion''s turn, places a [Counterattack] buff on them for 1 turn.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: At the start of each round, places a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 1 turn. This buff cannot be removed. At the end of this Champion''s turn, places a [Counterattack] buff on them for 1 turn.'),
  ('351986f9-9140-4c05-8451-a7b2d6b1351a','C000878-A1','A1','base','Torturous Bolts','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. Each hit has a 50% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns.','0','0','2.1','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. Each hit has a 50% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Damage Multiplier: 2.1 ATK'),
  ('351986f9-9140-4c05-8451-a7b2d6b1351a','C000878-A2','A2','base','Purge The Impure','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, removes all buffs from all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a [Block Buffs] debuff and a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns.','5','3','6','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, removes all buffs from all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a [Block Buffs] debuff and a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Level 6: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 6 ATK'),
  ('351986f9-9140-4c05-8451-a7b2d6b1351a','C000878-A3','A3','base','Mother Knows Best','Revives all dead allies with 50% HP and 50% Turn Meter. If all other allies are dead, revives them with 75% HP and 75% Turn Meter instead, and decreases the cooldown of all revived ally skills by 1 turn. Also increases the cooldown of all enemy skills by 2 turns.','6','4',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Revives all dead allies with 50% HP and 50% Turn Meter. If all other allies are dead, revives them with 75% HP and 75% Turn Meter instead, and decreases the cooldown of all revived ally skills by 1 turn. Also increases the cooldown of all enemy skills by 2 turns. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('351986f9-9140-4c05-8451-a7b2d6b1351a','C000878-P','Passive','base','Warped Benevolence','Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 20% whenever an ally dies. Heals this Champion by 20% of their MAX HP whenever they are attacked by an enemy under a [Pain Link] debuff. Occurs once per turn. Places a [Pain Link] debuff for 2 turns on enemies who deal damage equal to 25% or more of an ally''s MAX HP with a single skill. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 20% whenever an ally dies. Heals this Champion by 20% of their MAX HP whenever they are attacked by an enemy under a [Pain Link] debuff. Occurs once per turn. Places a [Pain Link] debuff for 2 turns on enemies who deal damage equal to 25% or more of an ally''s MAX HP with a single skill. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. Heal Multiplier: 0.2 HP'),
  ('d6595122-41cc-467c-b734-5eccc1a7dd6a','C000882-A1','A1','base','Raging River','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Before attacking, has a 50% chance of removing all buffs from the target. Has a 100% chance to steal all buffs instead if this skill is used not on this Champion''s turn. This effect cannot be resisted by targets whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s. Will ignore 5% of the target''s DEF for each buff on this Champion.','0','0','1.7','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Before attacking, has a 50% chance of removing all buffs from the target. Has a 100% chance to steal all buffs instead if this skill is used not on this Champion''s turn. This effect cannot be resisted by targets whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s. Will ignore 5% of the target''s DEF for each buff on this Champion. Level 2: Damage +20% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Damage Multiplier: 1.7 ATK'),
  ('d6595122-41cc-467c-b734-5eccc1a7dd6a','C000882-A2','A2','base','Erosive Force','Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 15% [Shatter] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Will ignore [Block Damage] and [Stone Skin] buffs. Grants an Extra Turn if this attack kills an enemy. If the target survives, fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 30% instead.','5','4','5.2','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 15% [Shatter] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Will ignore [Block Damage] and [Stone Skin] buffs. Grants an Extra Turn if this attack kills an enemy. If the target survives, fills the Turn Meters of all allies by 30% instead. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 5.2 ATK'),
  ('d6595122-41cc-467c-b734-5eccc1a7dd6a','C000882-A3','A3','base','Meltwater Flood','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, has a 75% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be resisted by targets whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s. Will ignore 25% of each target''s DEF. Places an extra hit on enemies whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s. Places an [Unkillable] buff and a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 2 turns.','6','4','3','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, has a 75% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff on all enemies for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be resisted by targets whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s. Will ignore 25% of each target''s DEF. Places an extra hit on enemies whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s. Places an [Unkillable] buff and a [Counterattack] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +20% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Level 6: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 3 ATK'),
  ('d6595122-41cc-467c-b734-5eccc1a7dd6a','C000882-P','Passive','base','Student Of Glaicad','Has a 50% chance to deal 100% more damage against enemies whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s. This Champion receives 30% less damage from enemies whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Has a 50% chance to deal 100% more damage against enemies whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s. This Champion receives 30% less damage from enemies whose ATK is equal to or lower than this Champion''s.'),
  ('ea019155-b47d-42a1-923f-728a093e7d77','C000884-A1','A1','base','Holy Terror','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. The first hit heals this Champion by 30% of the damage inflicted. The second hit has a 65% chance of placing a [True Fear] debuff for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be resisted if the first hit fully healed this Champion. If the target is a Boss, the second hit has a 65% chance of placing a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns instead.','0','0','1.7','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. The first hit heals this Champion by 30% of the damage inflicted. The second hit has a 65% chance of placing a [True Fear] debuff for 1 turn. This debuff cannot be resisted if the first hit fully healed this Champion. If the target is a Boss, the second hit has a 65% chance of placing a 30% [Decrease SPD] debuff for 2 turns instead. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Damage Multiplier: 1.7 ATK'),
  ('ea019155-b47d-42a1-923f-728a093e7d77','C000884-A2','A2','base','Storm of Righteousness','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, removes all [Increase DEF], [Ally Protection], and [Strengthen] buffs from all enemies. This effect cannot be resisted. If at least one buff was removed, also places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 30% [Increase C. DMG] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Will also ignore 30% of each target''s DEF. Boosts this Champion''s Turn Meter by 30% for each enemy alive after the attack.','5','4','3.1','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, removes all [Increase DEF], [Ally Protection], and [Strengthen] buffs from all enemies. This effect cannot be resisted. If at least one buff was removed, also places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 30% [Increase C. DMG] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. Will also ignore 30% of each target''s DEF. Boosts this Champion''s Turn Meter by 30% for each enemy alive after the attack. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 3.1 ATK'),
  ('ea019155-b47d-42a1-923f-728a093e7d77','C000884-A3','A3','base','By My Hand!','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit ignores 30% of the target''s DEF and destroys the enemy''s MAX HP by 25% of the damage dealt. Cannot destroy a single enemy''s MAX HP by more than 75%. If the target is a Boss, destroys MAX HP equal to 35% of the damage dealt. If the target has any active skills on cooldown, both hits will ignore 50% of the target''s DEF instead. Ignores [Shield], [Unkillable], and [Block Damage] buffs.','4','3','2.5','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Each hit ignores 30% of the target''s DEF and destroys the enemy''s MAX HP by 25% of the damage dealt. Cannot destroy a single enemy''s MAX HP by more than 75%. If the target is a Boss, destroys MAX HP equal to 35% of the damage dealt. If the target has any active skills on cooldown, both hits will ignore 50% of the target''s DEF instead. Ignores [Shield], [Unkillable], and [Block Damage] buffs. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 2.5 ATK'),
  ('ea019155-b47d-42a1-923f-728a093e7d77','C000884-P','Passive','base','Inexorable','Instantly resets the cooldown on one of this Champion''s random active skills, whenever an enemy increases the cooldown of any of their skills. Grants an Extra Turn if a skill''s cooldown was reset. After granting an Extra Turn, places this skill on cooldown. Will also grant an Extra Turn if an ally, Mastery, Artifact Set, or Accessory decreases the cooldown of any of this Champion''s skills. After granting an Extra Turn, places this skill on cooldown.','4','4',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Instantly resets the cooldown on one of this Champion''s random active skills, whenever an enemy increases the cooldown of any of their skills. Grants an Extra Turn if a skill''s cooldown was reset. After granting an Extra Turn, places this skill on cooldown. Will also grant an Extra Turn if an ally, Mastery, Artifact Set, or Accessory decreases the cooldown of any of this Champion''s skills. After granting an Extra Turn, places this skill on cooldown.'),
  ('66c6c097-12b8-4db4-a6ce-9be33574d825','C000886-A1','A1','base','Render Flesh','Attacks all enemies. Has a 35% chance of instantly activating any [Poison] and [HP Burn] debuffs on each enemy.','0','0','0.16','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Has a 35% chance of instantly activating any [Poison] and [HP Burn] debuffs on each enemy. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +5% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 0.16 HP'),
  ('66c6c097-12b8-4db4-a6ce-9be33574d825','C000886-A2','A2','base','Venge-fire','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing two 5% [Poison] debuffs and a [HP Burn] debuff for 2 turns.','4','3','0.26','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing two 5% [Poison] debuffs and a [HP Burn] debuff for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 0.26 HP'),
  ('66c6c097-12b8-4db4-a6ce-9be33574d825','C000886-A3','A3','base','Despoiler of Anhelt','Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Then increases the duration of all enemy debuffs by 1 turn. Also decreases the duration of all ally debuffs by 1 turn. [Ogryn Tribes Unity: 1 Faction ally: Places a 30% Increase SPD buff on all allies for 2 turns. 2 Faction allies: Increases the duration of all enemy debuffs for 2 turns and decreases the duration of all ally debuffs by 2 turns instead. 3 Faction allies: Heals all allies by 5% of this Champion''s MAX HP, +2% (up to 50%) for every enemy debuff extended and ally debuff shortened by this skill.]','5','3','0.29','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ACC] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Then increases the duration of all enemy debuffs by 1 turn. Also decreases the duration of all ally debuffs by 1 turn. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 0.29 HP [Ogryn Tribes Unity: 1 Faction ally: Places a 30% Increase SPD buff on all allies for 2 turns. 2 Faction allies: Increases the duration of all enemy debuffs for 2 turns and decreases the duration of all ally debuffs by 2 turns instead. 3 Faction allies: Heals all allies by 5% of this Champion''s MAX HP, +2% (up to 50%) for every enemy debuff extended and ally debuff shortened by this skill.]'),
  ('66c6c097-12b8-4db4-a6ce-9be33574d825','C000886-P','Passive','base','Bonegrinder Brand','Increases each ally''s ACC by 10 for each [HP Burn] and [Poison] debuff on the enemy team. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. [Ogryn Tribes Unity: 1 Faction ally: HP Burn and Poison debuffs placed by allies deal 30% more damage. 2 Faction allies: Increases damage dealt by enemies by 5% for each HP Burn and Poison debuff on a target. 3 Faction allies: HP Burn and Poison debuffs placed by allies cannot be removed, stolen, or transferred.]','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Increases each ally''s ACC by 10 for each [HP Burn] and [Poison] debuff on the enemy team. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. [Ogryn Tribes Unity: 1 Faction ally: HP Burn and Poison debuffs placed by allies deal 30% more damage. 2 Faction allies: Increases damage dealt by enemies by 5% for each HP Burn and Poison debuff on a target. 3 Faction allies: HP Burn and Poison debuffs placed by allies cannot be removed, stolen, or transferred.]'),
  ('848fb652-fb54-4912-b71a-0abce5779e63','C000888-A1','A1','base','Molten Blade','Attacks 1 enemy. Each time this skill is used, permanently increases the damage inflicted by this skill by 10% [stacks up to 100%]. Counterattacks with this skill each time an enemy under a [HP Burn] debuff attacks this Champion or their allies.','0','0','3.5','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Each time this skill is used, permanently increases the damage inflicted by this skill by 10% [stacks up to 100%]. Counterattacks with this skill each time an enemy under a [HP Burn] debuff attacks this Champion or their allies. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Damage Multiplier: 3.5 DEF'),
  ('848fb652-fb54-4912-b71a-0abce5779e63','C000888-A2','A2','base','Flaming Terror','Attacks all enemies. Places a [Fear] debuff for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be resisted by enemies under a [HP Burn] debuff.','4','3','3.6','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Places a [Fear] debuff for 2 turns. This debuff cannot be resisted by enemies under a [HP Burn] debuff. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 3.6 DEF'),
  ('848fb652-fb54-4912-b71a-0abce5779e63','C000888-A3','A3','base','Demolition Burn','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. The damage inflicted by this skill increases by 10% for the turns left remaining of any [HP Burn] debuffs on the target [stacks up to 100%]. [Demonspawn Unity: 1 Faction Ally: Damage received decreased by 50% while this skill is not on cooldown. 2 Faction Ally: Each HP Burn activation on an enemy has 50% chance to decrease this skill''s cooldown by 1. 3 Faction Ally: If target is under HP Burn, ignores Stone Skin, Unkillable, Ally Protection, Block Damage and Shield buffs.]','4','4','(3 + (0.3 Total Burn Duration on Enemies)) DEF','formula',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. The damage inflicted by this skill increases by 10% for the turns left remaining of any [HP Burn] debuffs on the target [stacks up to 100%]. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Damage +10% Damage Multiplier: (3 + (0.3 Total Burn Duration on Enemies)) DEF [Demonspawn Unity: 1 Faction Ally: Damage received decreased by 50% while this skill is not on cooldown. 2 Faction Ally: Each HP Burn activation on an enemy has 50% chance to decrease this skill''s cooldown by 1. 3 Faction Ally: If target is under HP Burn, ignores Stone Skin, Unkillable, Ally Protection, Block Damage and Shield buffs.]'),
  ('848fb652-fb54-4912-b71a-0abce5779e63','C000888-P','Passive','base','Surging Demonfyre','Whenever an enemy receives a buff or has their Turn Meter increased, has a 50% chance to place a [HP Burn] debuff, has a 50% chance to instantly activate it instead. [Demonspawn Unity: 1 Faction Ally: HP Burn placed by this skill cannot be resisted or blocked. 2 Faction Ally: Each HP Burn activation grants 5% Ignore DEF (up to 100%). 3 Faction Ally: Places Block Revive on enemies killed under HP Burn.]','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Whenever an enemy receives a buff or has their Turn Meter increased, has a 50% chance to place a [HP Burn] debuff, has a 50% chance to instantly activate it instead. Level 2: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% [Demonspawn Unity: 1 Faction Ally: HP Burn placed by this skill cannot be resisted or blocked. 2 Faction Ally: Each HP Burn activation grants 5% Ignore DEF (up to 100%). 3 Faction Ally: Places Block Revive on enemies killed under HP Burn.]'),
  ('0a442031-0625-4684-bacb-565c9ee5617f','C000890-A1','A1','base','Skyfall Arrow','Attacks all enemies. This attack will not trigger counterattacks. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 5% for each living enemy after the attack.','0','0','2.5','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. This attack will not trigger counterattacks. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 5% for each living enemy after the attack. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Damage +5% Level 4: Damage +5% Level 5: Damage +5% Damage Multiplier: 2.5 ATK'),
  ('0a442031-0625-4684-bacb-565c9ee5617f','C000890-A2','A2','base','Falcon Shot','Attacks all enemies 2 times. The first hit has a 75% chance of placing a [Block Buffs] debuff for 2 turns. The second hit has a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 5% for each living enemy after the attack.','4','3','1.5 ATK + 0.035 Enemy Max HP','formula',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies 2 times. The first hit has a 75% chance of placing a [Block Buffs] debuff for 2 turns. The second hit has a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns. Fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 5% for each living enemy after the attack. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Level 6: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 1.5 ATK + 0.035 Enemy Max HP'),
  ('0a442031-0625-4684-bacb-565c9ee5617f','C000890-A3','A3','base','Forever Marked','Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff, a 50% [Increase ACC] buff and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on this Champion for 3 turns. Then grants an Extra Turn.','6','4',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff, a 50% [Increase ACC] buff and a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on this Champion for 3 turns. Then grants an Extra Turn. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('0a442031-0625-4684-bacb-565c9ee5617f','C000890-P','Passive','base','No Foe Too Great','Increases this Champion''s MAX HP by 20% for each enemy killed or Hydra Head decapitated by this Champion (stacks up to 50,000).','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Increases this Champion''s MAX HP by 20% for each enemy killed or Hydra Head decapitated by this Champion (stacks up to 50,000).'),
  ('7023ffea-67b9-42e8-9b46-87d9aac33a08','C000894-A1','A1','base','Corruption Scepter','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 30% chance of randomly increasing the cooldown of one of the target''s skills by 2 turns. This effect cannot be resisted if Wight Queen Ankora is on the same team.','0','0','0.24','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 30% chance of randomly increasing the cooldown of one of the target''s skills by 2 turns. This effect cannot be resisted if Wight Queen Ankora is on the same team. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 0.24 HP'),
  ('7023ffea-67b9-42e8-9b46-87d9aac33a08','C000894-A2','A2','base','Desecration Blast','Attacks all enemies. Will ignore 25% of the target''s DEF. Places an extra hit on targets under [Shield] or [Strengthen] buffs. Damage inflicted by this skill cannot be decreased by enemy Passive skills or Masteries, except by the Passive skills of Bosses. Damage inflicted by this skill cannot be increased by either this Champion''s Masteries or ally Passive skills, except when attacking Bosses.','4','3','0.28','HP',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Will ignore 25% of the target''s DEF. Places an extra hit on targets under [Shield] or [Strengthen] buffs. Damage inflicted by this skill cannot be decreased by enemy Passive skills or Masteries, except by the Passive skills of Bosses. Damage inflicted by this skill cannot be increased by either this Champion''s Masteries or ally Passive skills, except when attacking Bosses. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 0.28 HP'),
  ('7023ffea-67b9-42e8-9b46-87d9aac33a08','C000894-A3','A3','base','Spirits, Claim You','Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Increases the damage inflicted with this skill by 10% for each buff on the target (stacks up to 50%) and by an additional 10% for each buff on this Champion (stacks up to 50%). If this attack kills a target under 3 or more buffs, places a [Block Revive] debuff. Also grants an Extra Turn if this attack kills an enemy when Wight Queen Ankora is on the same team.','5','5','0.2 HP + (0.2 HP * 0.1 * Total Active Buffs on Target) + (0.2 HP * 0.1 * Total Active Buffs on Self)','formula',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 2 times. Increases the damage inflicted with this skill by 10% for each buff on the target (stacks up to 50%) and by an additional 10% for each buff on this Champion (stacks up to 50%). If this attack kills a target under 3 or more buffs, places a [Block Revive] debuff. Also grants an Extra Turn if this attack kills an enemy when Wight Queen Ankora is on the same team. Damage Multiplier: 0.2 HP + (0.2 HP * 0.1 * Total Active Buffs on Target) + (0.2 HP * 0.1 * Total Active Buffs on Self)'),
  ('7023ffea-67b9-42e8-9b46-87d9aac33a08','C000894-P','Passive','base','Mantle of Undeath','This Champion will receive 50% less damage when attacked by enemies, including Bosses and their minions, out of their active turn. If Wight Queen Ankora is on the same team, this champion will receive no damage when attacked by enemies out of their active turn. [This effect does not apply against bosses and their minions]. This champion will also ignore [Shield] and [Strengthen] buffs.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: This Champion will receive 50% less damage when attacked by enemies, including Bosses and their minions, out of their active turn. If Wight Queen Ankora is on the same team, this champion will receive no damage when attacked by enemies out of their active turn. [This effect does not apply against bosses and their minions]. This champion will also ignore [Shield] and [Strengthen] buffs.'),
  ('1eed375c-b9a6-45f2-95c7-545559efea5b','C000895-A1','A1','base','Necrobolt','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 30% chance of decreasing the cooldown of a random ally''s skill by 2 turns (except this Champion). If Wight King Narses is on the same team and has any active skills on cooldown, decreases the cooldown of one of their skills by 2 turns. If Wight King Narses is on the same team and has no active skill on cooldown, decreases the cooldown of a random ally''s skill by 2 turns except this Champion. If the cooldown on a skill is fully reset, also heals that ally by 10% of this Champion''s MAX HP.','0','0','5.6','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 30% chance of decreasing the cooldown of a random ally''s skill by 2 turns (except this Champion). If Wight King Narses is on the same team and has any active skills on cooldown, decreases the cooldown of one of their skills by 2 turns. If Wight King Narses is on the same team and has no active skill on cooldown, decreases the cooldown of a random ally''s skill by 2 turns except this Champion. If the cooldown on a skill is fully reset, also heals that ally by 10% of this Champion''s MAX HP. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 5.6 ATK'),
  ('1eed375c-b9a6-45f2-95c7-545559efea5b','C000895-A2','A2','base','Shield of Emaria','Removes all debuffs from all allies, and places a [Shield] buff on them equal to 25% of this Champion''s MAX HP for 2 turns. If Wight King Narses is on the same team, also places a 25% [Strengthen] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Then, fills the turn meters of all allies by 10%.','4','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Removes all debuffs from all allies, and places a [Shield] buff on them equal to 25% of this Champion''s MAX HP for 2 turns. If Wight King Narses is on the same team, also places a 25% [Strengthen] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Then, fills the turn meters of all allies by 10%. Level 2: Shield +10% Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('1eed375c-b9a6-45f2-95c7-545559efea5b','C000895-A3','A3','base','Rise, My Love','Revives a dead ally with 50% HP and 75% Turn Meter. Resets the cooldowns of the revived ally''s skills. If the target is Wight King Narses, revives them with 75% HP and 100% Turn Meter instead. After the revival, decreases the Turn Meters of all enemies by 10%. If Wight King Narses is revived, decreases the turn meters of all enemies by 20% instead. This effect cannot be resisted.','5','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Revives a dead ally with 50% HP and 75% Turn Meter. Resets the cooldowns of the revived ally''s skills. If the target is Wight King Narses, revives them with 75% HP and 100% Turn Meter instead. After the revival, decreases the Turn Meters of all enemies by 10%. If Wight King Narses is revived, decreases the turn meters of all enemies by 20% instead. This effect cannot be resisted. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('1eed375c-b9a6-45f2-95c7-545559efea5b','C000895-P','Passive','base','Queen Consort','Whenever an enemy tries to place a [Fear], [True Fear], [Freeze], [Provoke], [Sleep], [Stun], or [Petrification] debuff on the ally with the highest C.DMG, transfer those debuffs to this Champion instead. Fills the Turn Meter of this Champion by 50% if this Champion misses their turn due to one of these debuffs. At the start of this Champion''s turn, remove any [Fear], [True Fear], [Freeze], [Provoke], [Sleep], [Stun], or [Petrification] debuffs from this Champion, if Wight King Narses is on the same team. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.','3','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Whenever an enemy tries to place a [Fear], [True Fear], [Freeze], [Provoke], [Sleep], [Stun], or [Petrification] debuff on the ally with the highest C.DMG, transfer those debuffs to this Champion instead. Fills the Turn Meter of this Champion by 50% if this Champion misses their turn due to one of these debuffs. At the start of this Champion''s turn, remove any [Fear], [True Fear], [Freeze], [Provoke], [Sleep], [Stun], or [Petrification] debuffs from this Champion, if Wight King Narses is on the same team. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1 Level 4: Cooldown -1'),
  ('ba782124-c3b1-4b06-87d0-0cb78ca282bf','C000900-A1','A1','base','Bejeweled Club','Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 40% chance of decreasing the cooldown of a random ally''s skill by 1 turn. Cannot decrease this Champion''s cooldowns. Also heals the ally who had their skill cooldown decreased by 10% of this Champion''s MAX HP.','0','0','3.8','DEF',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy. Has a 40% chance of decreasing the cooldown of a random ally''s skill by 1 turn. Cannot decrease this Champion''s cooldowns. Also heals the ally who had their skill cooldown decreased by 10% of this Champion''s MAX HP. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Damage +5% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 3.8 DEF'),
  ('ba782124-c3b1-4b06-87d0-0cb78ca282bf','C000900-A2','A2','base','Primeval Secret','Places an [Unkillable] buff and a [Counterattack] buff on a single ally for 2 turns. Also decreases the cooldown of all that ally''s skills by 2 turns. This skill''s cooldown cannot be decreased or reset.','5','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Places an [Unkillable] buff and a [Counterattack] buff on a single ally for 2 turns. Also decreases the cooldown of all that ally''s skills by 2 turns. This skill''s cooldown cannot be decreased or reset. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('ba782124-c3b1-4b06-87d0-0cb78ca282bf','C000900-A3','A3','base','Coccoon Of Revival','Revives a single ally with 50% HP and 75% Turn Meter. Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 60% [Increase DEF] buff on that ally for 2 turns.','6','4',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Revives a single ally with 50% HP and 75% Turn Meter. Places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff and a 60% [Increase DEF] buff on that ally for 2 turns. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('ba782124-c3b1-4b06-87d0-0cb78ca282bf','C000900-P','Passive','base','Temporal Scholar','Whenever an enemy Champion''s passive skill activates, fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 30%. Occurs once per turn.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Whenever an enemy Champion''s passive skill activates, fills this Champion''s Turn Meter by 30%. Occurs once per turn.'),
  ('c923f52d-7e82-46a3-9794-abc62a0abddb','C000903-A1','A1','base','Battle Catalyst','Attacks all enemies. Has a 50% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns. The ally with the highest C.DMG also joins to attack the enemy with the lowest HP. The ally joining the attack will use their default skill.','0','0','3','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Has a 50% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns. The ally with the highest C.DMG also joins to attack the enemy with the lowest HP. The ally joining the attack will use their default skill. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 4: Damage +5% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Damage Multiplier: 3 ATK'),
  ('c923f52d-7e82-46a3-9794-abc62a0abddb','C000903-A2','A2','base','Fumes of the Grail','Places a [Poison Cloud] buff, a 30% [Increase SPD] buff and two 15% [Continuous Heal] buffs on a target ally for 2 turns. Also fills the target''s Turn Meter by 50%.','5','3',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Places a [Poison Cloud] buff, a 30% [Increase SPD] buff and two 15% [Continuous Heal] buffs on a target ally for 2 turns. Also fills the target''s Turn Meter by 50%. Level 2: Cooldown -1 Level 3: Cooldown -1'),
  ('c923f52d-7e82-46a3-9794-abc62a0abddb','C000903-A3','A3','base','Malignant Growth','Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff and a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. Will ignore [Block Debuffs] buffs.','5','3','4.5','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Has a 75% chance of placing a 60% [Decrease DEF] debuff and a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. Will ignore [Block Debuffs] buffs. Level 2: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 3: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 4.5 ATK'),
  ('c923f52d-7e82-46a3-9794-abc62a0abddb','C000903-P','Passive','base','Yncensed','Increases this Champion''s ACC by 10 for each buff on each enemy. Whenever an enemy receives a buff, their Turn Meter is decreased by 10%.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Increases this Champion''s ACC by 10 for each buff on each enemy. Whenever an enemy receives a buff, their Turn Meter is decreased by 10%.'),
  ('e0945e88-df9c-4a07-968d-b431c5c22c0a','C000908-A1','A1','base','Blade Combo','Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. Has a 30% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns.','0','0','1.2','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 3 times. Has a 30% chance of placing a 25% [Weaken] debuff for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Damage +5% Level 4: Damage +10% Damage Multiplier: 1.2 ATK'),
  ('e0945e88-df9c-4a07-968d-b431c5c22c0a','C000908-A2','A2','base','Blade Strike','Attacks 1 enemy 4 times. Each hit increases this Champion''s Turn Meter by 5%. Also places a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on all allies for 2 turns.','4','3','1.4','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 4 times. Each hit increases this Champion''s Turn Meter by 5%. Also places a 30% [Increase SPD] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 1.4 ATK'),
  ('e0945e88-df9c-4a07-968d-b431c5c22c0a','C000908-A3','A3','base','Blade Spin','Attacks 1 enemy 4 times. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The first and the second hit each have a 75% chance of placing a [Leech] debuff for 2 turns. The third and the fourth hit each have a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns.','4','3','1.5','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: Attacks 1 enemy 4 times. Before attacking, places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on this Champion for 2 turns. The first and the second hit each have a 75% chance of placing a [Leech] debuff for 2 turns. The third and the fourth hit each have a 75% chance of placing a 50% [Decrease ATK] debuff for 2 turns. Level 2: Damage +10% Level 3: Damage +10% Level 4: Buff/Debuff Chance +10% Level 5: Buff/Debuff Chance +15% Level 6: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 1.5 ATK'),
  ('e0945e88-df9c-4a07-968d-b431c5c22c0a','C000908-P','Passive','base','Zinogre Essence','[Passive Effect] Increases the damage this Champion deals by 1% for every 1% of HP lost (stacks up to 50%). This increased damage doubles if a target is under a [Decrease DEF] debuff. [Active Effect] Prevents this Champion''s death and keeps them alive on 1 HP when hit by a fatal hit. If this skill prevents this Champion''s death, heals them by 50% of their MAX HP. Will not prevent this Champion''s death if they are under a [Heal Reduction] debuff.','4','4',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','skill text from ayumilove guide page | verbatim: [Passive Effect] Increases the damage this Champion deals by 1% for every 1% of HP lost (stacks up to 50%). This increased damage doubles if a target is under a [Decrease DEF] debuff. [Active Effect] Prevents this Champion''s death and keeps them alive on 1 HP when hit by a fatal hit. If this skill prevents this Champion''s death, heals them by 50% of their MAX HP. Will not prevent this Champion''s death if they are under a [Heal Reduction] debuff.'),
  ('ead0c0c2-1cea-492a-983f-1900bd243455','C000782-A3','A3','base','Shield of the Clans','Places a 50% [Increase RES] buff and a 30% [Reflect Damage] buff on all allies for 2 turns.','5','4',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','rework/defect fix from ayumilove guide | verbatim: Places a 50% [Increase RES] buff and a 30% [Reflect Damage] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Level 2: Cooldown -1'),
  ('ead0c0c2-1cea-492a-983f-1900bd243455','C000782-P','Passive','base','Brawny Surge','This Champion''s RES is increased by 50 whenever their active skills are not on cooldown.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','rework/defect fix from ayumilove guide | verbatim: This Champion''s RES is increased by 50 whenever their active skills are not on cooldown.'),
  ('599ae220-021a-4cb3-99d1-f07513f3b8ff','C000407-A3','A3','base','First to Fight','Attacks all enemies. Places a 30% [Increase C.DMG] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on all allies if this attack is critical.','5','4','3.2','ATK',0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','rework/defect fix from ayumilove guide | verbatim: Attacks all enemies. Places a 30% [Increase C.DMG] buff on all allies for 2 turns. Also places a 50% [Increase ATK] buff on all allies if this attack is critical. Level 2: Damage +5% Level 3: Damage +5% Level 4: Damage +10% Level 5: Cooldown -1 Damage Multiplier: 3.2 ATK'),
  ('93561c28-d027-493c-9bba-d24704904791','C000750-P','Passive','base','Caustic Rebuttal','Whenever an ally is attacked, has a 25% chance of placing a 5% [Poison] debuff on the attacker for 2 turns. Whenever this Champion is attacked, the chance increases to 50%. Enemies under [Poison] debuffs inflict 5% less damage per each [Poison] debuff on them (stacks up to 25%). If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.','0','0',null,null,0,'web_sourced','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','rework/defect fix from ayumilove guide | verbatim: Whenever an ally is attacked, has a 25% chance of placing a 5% [Poison] debuff on the attacker for 2 turns. Whenever this Champion is attacked, the chance increases to 50%. Enemies under [Poison] debuffs inflict 5% less damage per each [Poison] debuff on them (stacks up to 25%). If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.'),
  ('7c238bd2-344e-497f-b23d-645c05feddc4','C000780-P','Passive','base','Nergigante Ambition','Heals all allies by 10% of their MAX HP when attacking enemies under a [Hex] debuff. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate. Increases this Champion''s DEF by 5% each time this Champion receives a hit from an enemy under a [Hex] debuff (stacks up to 30%).',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('3c2bf748-c572-48e0-b506-1b4464a4ef9e','C000783-P','Passive','base','Art of Stealth','At the start of each turn, places a [Perfect Veil] buff for 1 turn on the ally with the highest ATK. Inflicts 20% more damage against targets whose DEF is lower than this Champion''s DEF.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('68392117-d44b-4b7a-bd8b-b5308ce8c8df','C000817-P','Passive','base','Equitable','Whenever this Champion is attacked, has a 20% chance of decreasing the duration of all buffs on the attacker by 1 turn. Has a 40% chance instead when attacked by a Boss.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('dc1a1273-88b7-43e6-9fb7-64f9f17620ed','C000828-P','Passive','base','Rigged To Blow','The damage inflicted by [Poison] and [HP Burn] debuffs will ignore [Block Damage] and [Unkillable] buffs. Whenever allies attack enemies with destroyed MAX HP, increases the damage dealt by 10%. If there are multiple Champions on the team with this skill, only one will activate.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('f69c408d-e48a-4439-b15b-645403c22b70','C000839-P','Passive','base','Earned Resilience','Decreases the damage this Champion receives by 10% for each ally under an [Ally Protection] buff. This Champion is immune to [Pain Link] debuffs, as well as any damage from [Reflect Damage] buffs or passive Reflect Damage effects.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11'),
  ('75390a65-4b29-4c13-a906-d0990ca28ea0','C000842-P','Passive','base','Heightened Senses','Immune to [Sleep] debuffs. Increases this Champion''s ACC by 10 and C.DMG by 3% for each buff on the enemy team.',null,null,null,null,0,'pending','worksheet Skills tab 2026-07-11','Rebuilt from ayumilove verbatim 2026-07-11')
